Matt. 1:1 ¶ Hih in Zeisu Khazih khang ciamtehna ahi hi. Amah in David tapa hi a, David in Abraham tapa ahi hi.
Matt. 1:2 Abraham tapa Isaac, Isaac tapa Jacob, Jacob tapa Judah le a sanggam pasal teng ahi hi.
Matt. 1:3 Judah in Tamar tawh a neih a tapa Perez le Zerah, Perez tapa Hezron, Hezron tapa Ram,
Matt. 1:4 Ram tapa Amminadab, Amminadab tapa Nahshon, Nahshon tapa Salmon,
Matt. 1:5 Salmon in a zi Rahab tawh a neih a tapa Boaz, Boaz in a zi Ruth tawh a neih a tapa Obed, Obed tapa Jesse,
Matt. 1:6 Jesse tapa kumpipa David ahi hi. ¶ David in Uriah zi tawh a neih a tapa Solomon,
Matt. 1:7 Solomon tapa Rehoboam, Rehoboam tapa Abijah, Abijah tapa Asa,
Matt. 1:8 Asa tapa Jehoshaphat, Jehoshaphat tapa Joram, Joram tapa Uzziah,
Matt. 1:9 Uzziah tapa Jotham, Jotham tapa Ahaz, Ahaz tapa Hezekiah,
Matt. 1:10 Hezekiah tapa Manasseh, Manasseh tapa Amon, Amon tapa Josiah ahi hi.
Matt. 1:11 Jeconiah le a sanggam pasal tengin Babylon gam ah sala a kipaipih madeuh in a suak Josiah tate ahi uh hi.
Matt. 1:12 ¶ Babylon gama saltan khit ciangin Jeconiah in a neih a tapa Shealtiel, Shealtiel tapa Zerubbabel,
Matt. 1:13 Zerubbabel tapa Abiud, Abiud tapa Eliakim, Eliakim tapa Azor,
Matt. 1:14 Azor tapa Zadok, Zadok tapa Achim, Achim tapa Eliud,
Matt. 1:15 Eliud tapa Eleazar, Eleazar tapa Matthan, Matthan tapa Jacob,
Matt. 1:16 Jacob tapa Joseph hi a, Joseph in Khazih a kici Zeisu a hong suahna Mary pasal ahi hi.
Matt. 1:17 ¶ Tua hi a, Abraham khang panin David khang ciang a vekin khang sawm le khang li, David khang panin Babylon gama saltang dinga a kimat hun ciang khang sawm le khang li, Babylon gama saltan hun pan Khazih khang ciang khang sawm le khang li mah ahi hi.
Matt. 1:18 ¶ Zeisu Khazih a suah zia hih bang ahi hi. A nu Mary pen Joseph zi dingin zuthawl kipiasa hi a, a kiteen ma un Kha Siangtho hangin a gai hi.
Matt. 1:19 A lawmpa Joseph in mi dik hi a, a lawmnu Mary min daisak nuam lo ahih manin maksim dingin a ngaihsun hi.
Matt. 1:20 ¶ Tua banga a ngaihsut laitakin Topa vantungmi khat a mang sungah kilang a, “David tapa Joseph aw, na lawmnu Mary na teenpih ding lauthawng kei in; banghang hiam cihleh a sunga a paai nau pen Kha Siangtho hangin nau a paai ahi hi.
Matt. 1:21 Amah in tapa khat nei ding a, tua tapa in ama mite a mawhna panun honkhia ding ahih manin a min ZEISU na phuak ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 1:22 ¶ Topa in kamsangpa tunga a gensa thu a tangtun nadingin hih thu khempeuh a piang ahi hi.
Matt. 1:23 Kamsangpa in, “Ngai un, nungak siangtho khat gai in Tapa khat nei ding a, ama min Immanuel kici ding hi,” a ci hi. ¶ Immanuel a khiatna in, “Eite tawh Pasian hong omkhawm hi,” a cihna ahi hi.
Matt. 1:24 ¶ Joseph a ihmutna panin khanglo a, Topa vantungmi thupiakna bangin a lawmnu a teenpih hi.
Matt. 1:25 Ahi zongin tua a tacil a suah khit matengin a lawmnu luppih lo a, a suah ciangin a min dingin ZEISU a phuak hi.
Matt. 2:1 ¶ Kumpipa Herod a man laitakin Judea gam Bethlehem khua ah Zeisu a suak hi. A suah khit ciangin en in, nisuahna lam pana hong pai mi pilte Jerusalem khuapi hong tung uh hi.
Matt. 2:2 Amaute in, “Judah mite Kumpi dinga hong suakpa koi ah om ahi hiam? Nisuahna lam panin ama aksi ka muh uh ciangin amah bia dingin kong pai uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 2:3 ¶ Kumpipa Herod in tua thu a zak ciangin Jerusalem khua mi khempeuh tawh a patau mahmah uh hi.
Matt. 2:4 Herod in siampi liante le thukhamhilh siate khempeuh kaikhawm in Khazih suah nading mun a dong hi.
Matt. 2:5 Amaute in, “Judea gam Bethlehem khua ah a suak ding hi; banghang hiam cihleh kamsangpa in,
Matt. 2:6 ‘Judah gam Bethlehem khua aw, Judah gam ukpite lakah khuaneu khua gina lo pen na hi kei hi. Banghang hiam cihleh keima mi Israelte a cing ding Ukpa khat nangma sung panin a piang ding hi,’ ci in a gelh khinzo hi,” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 2:7 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Herod in mi pilte samsim a, aksi kilat hun teltakin a dong hi.
Matt. 2:8 Amah in Bethlehem khua ah amaute sawl a, “Pai unla, tua naupangno va mukhia hamtang un. Kei zong pai in ka va biak theih nadingin na muh khit uh ciangin kei kiangah hong zasakkik un,” a ci hi.
Matt. 2:9 ¶ Amaute in kumpipa vaikhakna a zak khit uh ciangin a paikhia uh hi. Tua ciangin nisuahna lama a muhsa uh aksi in naupangno omna tung a tun masiah amaute mai ah a pai hi.
Matt. 2:10 Aksi a muh uh ciangin a lungdam mahmah uh hi.
Matt. 2:11 Inn sungah a lut uh ciangin naupangno le a nu Mary mu uh a, bokin amah a bia uh hi. A van manphate uh suahkhia in kham, paknamtui le paknamtui kha letsong in a pia uh hi.
Matt. 2:12 Herod kiangah a paikik nawh loh nadingun Pasian in amaute mang sungah hilh ahih manin lampi dang tawnin amaute gam ah a ciahkik uh hi.
Matt. 2:13 ¶ Mi pilte a ciah khit uh ciangin Topa vantungmi khat Joseph mang sungah va kilang a, “Tho inla, naupangno le a nu Egypt gam ah taipih in. Herod in naupangno that nuamin zong ding ahih manin nang kiangah thu kong zaksakkik mateng tualai ah va om phot un,” a ci hi.
Matt. 2:14 ¶ Joseph zong tho in naupangno le a nu zankimpi mahin Egypt gam ah a paikhiatpih hi.
Matt. 2:15 Herod a sih mateng tualai ah a va om uh hi. Hih in, “Egypt panin ka Tapa ka samkhia hi,” ci a, kamsangpa tungtawnin Topa gensa thu a tangtun nading ahi hi.
Matt. 2:16 ¶ Herod in mi pilte khemna a theih ciangin heh mahmah hi. Tua ahih manin mi pilte a dotna panin a hun ding seh a, Bethlehem khua le a kim gam sunga om pasalno kum nih le a nuaisiah khempeuh a thatsak hi.
Matt. 2:17 Kamsangpa Jeremiah in a gensa thu hihlai ah a tangtung hi. Amah in,
Matt. 2:18 “Ramah ah tamlawhna, kahna le nakpi in thumna aw kiza hi. Rachel in a tate kahkah a, Amaute om nawn lo ahih manin, A kihehnep ding a ut kei hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 2:19 ¶ Herod a sih khit ciangin, en in, Egypt gama om Joseph mang sungah Topa vantungmi khat a va kilang hi.
Matt. 2:20 Amah in, “Naupangno a that nuamte si khinzo ahih manin tho inla naupangno le a nu Israel gam ah ciahpih in,” a ci hi.
Matt. 2:21 ¶ Amah zong tho a, naupangno le a nu tawh Israel gam hong zuan uh hi.
Matt. 2:22 Archelaus in a pa Herod za luahin Judea gam uk hi cih thu a zak ciangin tua gam ah pai ngam lo a, Pasian in a mang sunga a hilhkholh mah bangin Galilee gam ah a pai hi.
Matt. 2:23 “Amah Nazareth mi kici ding hi,” ci a, kamsangte gensa thu a tangtun nadingin Nazareth kici khua ah hong pai in tualai ah a teeng hi.
Matt. 3:1 ¶ Tua hunin Judea gam gamlak ah Tuiphumpa John thuhilh in hong pai a,
Matt. 3:2 “Vantung kumpigam hong nai zo ahih manin na mawhna uh kisikkik un!” ci in a tangko hi.
Matt. 3:3 ¶ Kamsangpa Isaiah in, “Gamlak a kikopa awging in, ‘Topa pai nading lam na sial unla, Ama lampite na tangsak un,’ ci hi,” ci a a genpa in hih John ahi hi.
Matt. 3:4 ¶ John in kalaoh mul tawh a kigan puan silhin savun kawnggak tawh a kawng gak a, kauphe le gamlak khuaizu tawh a kivak hi.
Matt. 3:5 Tua hun sungin Jerusalem a kipan Judea gam sung khempeuh le Jordan Gun kuam mun khempeuh panin John kiangah mite a va pai uh hi.
Matt. 3:6 Amaute in a mawhnate uh pulakin John in Jordan Gun ah a tuiphum hi.
Matt. 3:7 ¶ Pharisee pawlte le Sadducee pawlte tampi tui kiphum dinga hong pai John in a muh ciangin amaute kiangah, “Gul gupha suante aw! Hong tung ding hehna panin a kihemkhia dingin kua in note hong hilhkhol ahi hiam?
Matt. 3:8 Tua ahih manin kisikkikna tawh a kituak gah na gah un.
Matt. 3:9 Note lungsim sungah, ‘Ka pa uh Abraham hi,’ ci in kimuang kha kei un; banghang hiam cihleh ken kong cih in ah Pasian in hih suangte nangawn Abraham tate a suaksak thei hi.
Matt. 3:10 Tu mahmahin zong singphung tengah hei kinga zo hi. Tua ahih manin gah hoih a gah lo singkung khempeuh kiphuk in meikuang sungah kikhul ding hi.
Matt. 3:11 ¶ “Kisikkikna tungtawnin note kong tuiphum hi. Ahi zongin kei khit cianga hong pai ding pa in kei sangin vanglian zaw a, ama khedap tawi dingin zong ka kilawm kei hi. Amah in Kha Siangtho le mei tawh note hong phum ding hi.
Matt. 3:12 Amah in a buhcilna tual hahsiang dingin a khut ah ansi zapna a tawi hi. Ama antak teng ansal sungah sung ding a, ansite ahih leh a mit ngei lo meikuang sungah a khul ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 3:13 ¶ Tua ciangin John tui kiphumsak dingin Galilee gam panin Jordan Gun ah Zeisu hong pai hi.
Matt. 3:14 Ahih hangin John in, “Nangmah in kei nong tuiphum ding hi zaw napi in banghang in kei kiangah hong pai zawsop na hi hiam?” ci in a mang nuam kei hi.
Matt. 3:15 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Thuman khempeuh i tangtungsak ding kilawm ahih manin tu in hong mang in,” a cih ciangin John in zong a mang hi.
Matt. 3:16 ¶ Zeisu tui a kiphum khit ciangin tui sung panin a dingto pah hi. Tua laitakin en in, vantung kihong a, Pasian Kha in vakhu bangin hong kumsuk in Zeisu tungah a khawl, John in a mu hi.
Matt. 3:17 Vantung pan thakhatin aw khat hong gingkhia a, “Hihpa in a hong lungdamsak mahmah ka it ka Tapa ahi hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:1 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Dawimangpa ze-etna thuak dingin Kha in gamlak ah Zeisu a paipih hi.
Matt. 4:2 Zeisu in sun 40 le zan 40 an a tan khit ciangin a gil a kial hi.
Matt. 4:3 Tua ciangin a ze-et ding pa ama kiangah va pai a, “Pasian Tapa na hih leh hih suangte anlum a suah nadingin thupia in,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:4 ¶ Ahih hangin Zeisu in, “ Lai Siangthosungah, ‘Mihing in an bek tawh a nungta hi loin Pasian kam panin a pusuak thu khempeuh tawh a nuntak ding ahi hi,’ ci in kigelh hi,” ci in a dawng hi.
Matt. 4:5 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Dawimangpa in khuapi siangtho sungah Zeisu lutpihin biakinnpi khumdawn ah a koih hi.
Matt. 4:6 Tua ciangin ama kiangah, “Pasian Tapa na hih leh lengkhiasuk in; banghang hiam cihleh, ‘Amah in nang hong kem dingin, Ama vantungmite thupia ding a, Na khe le suang a kitah khak loh nadingin, A khut uh tawh nang hong dom ding uh hi,’ ci in Lai Siangtho sungah kigelh hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:7 ¶ Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Lai Siangtho sungah, ‘Topa na Pasian na ze-et kei ding hi,’ ci in kigelh hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:8 ¶ Dawimangpa in mual sang mahmah khat dawn ah Zeisu paitohpih a, leitung kumpigam khempeuh le tuate thupina teng a vekpi in a lak hi.
Matt. 4:9 Tua ciangin ama kiangah, “Bokin hong bia leteh hih na khempeuh kong pia ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:10 ¶ Zeisu in ama kiangah, “ Satanaw, ka nungah kihemkhia in! ‘Topa na Pasian na bia ding a, ama na bek na sem ding hi,’ ci in Lai Siangtho sungah kigelh hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:11 ¶ Tua ciangin Dawimangpa in amah nusia a, en in, vantungmite hong pai in amah a kem uh hi.
Matt. 4:12 ¶ Thong sungah John a kikhiatna thu Zeisu in a zak ciangin Galilee gam ah a pai hi.
Matt. 4:13 Nazareth khua nusia in Zebulun le Naphtali gamnawl, tuilipi gei a om Capernaum khua ah a teeng hi.
Matt. 4:14 Tua in kamsangpa Isaiah gensa thu a tangtun nading ahi hi. Amah in,
Matt. 4:15 “Zebulun gam le Naphtali gamkete in, Jordan Gun gal tuili zuatna lampidung ah om a, Gentilete teenna, Galilee gamhuam ahi hi.
Matt. 4:16 Khuamial sunga tu tua mite in, A tang mahmah khuavak mu uh a, Sihna gam sung le sihna liim nuai a om, Tua mite tungah, Khuavak a tang ta hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:17 ¶ Tua hun a kipan Zeisu thuhilh kipan a, “Vantung kumpigam hong tung dekta ahih manin na mawhna uh kisikkik un,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:18 ¶ Galilee tuili gei ah Zeisu a pai laitakin unau nih mu a, Peter a kici Simon le a sanggampa Andrew ahi hi. Amaute ngabeng mi ahih manun tuili ah ngen khuhin a om uh hi.
Matt. 4:19 Tua ciangin amah in, “Ka nung hong zui un, note mi mante kong suaksak ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 4:20 ¶ Amaute in thakhatin a ngen uh nusia in Zeisu nung a zui uh hi.
Matt. 4:21 ¶ Tua mun pan a paikhiat ciangin a dang unau nihte a mu hi. Amaute in Zebedee tapa James le a sanggampa John hi a, a pa uh Zebedee tawh gunkuang sungah ngen khui in a om uh hi. Amah in amaute a sap ciangin,
Matt. 4:22 thakhatin a gunkuang le a pa uh nusia in amah a zui uh hi.
Matt. 4:23 ¶ Galilee gam sung tengah Zeisu vak kawikawi a, kikhopna innte ah thuhilh in kumpigam lungdamna thu a tangko hi. Amaute laka cinate le natna tuamtuam a nei khempeuh zong a damsak hi.
Matt. 4:24 Syria gam sung khempeuh ah a minthanna kizel in natna le zawngkhalna a tuamtuam a nei cina khempeuh le dawilutte, a sibup theite, pumzawte hong paipih uh a, amah in a damsak hi.
Matt. 4:25 Galilee gam, Decapolis gam, Jerusalem a kipan Judea gam le Jordan Gun gal panin hong pai mi honpi in amah a zui uh hi.
Matt. 5:1 ¶ Zeisu in mi honpite a muh ciangin mual tung ah kahto in tu a, ama kiangah a nungzuite in hong naih uh hi.
Matt. 5:2 Tua ciangin amah in thu a hilh in ah,
Matt. 5:3 “A lunggim mite in mi hampha ahi uh hi. Banghang hiam cihleh vantung kumpigam in amaute aa ahi hi.
Matt. 5:4 A dah a kapte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in hehnepna a ngah ding uh hi.
Matt. 5:5 A lungnemte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in leitung a luah ding uh hi.
Matt. 5:6 Gilkial dangtak banga dikna thu a lunggulhte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. Banghang hiam cihleh amaute a gilvah ding uh hi.
Matt. 5:7 Mi dang a hehpih theite in mi hampha ahi uh hi. Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in hehpihna a ngah ding uh hi.
Matt. 5:8 Lungsim siangthote in mi hampha ahi uh hi. Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in Pasian a mu ding uh hi.
Matt. 5:9 Kilemna a bawlte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. Banghang hiam cihleh amaute in Pasian tate cihna a ngah ding uh hi.
Matt. 5:10 Dikna thu hanga bawlsiatna a thuakte in mi hampha ahi uh hi. Banghang hiam cihleh vantung kumpigam in amaute aa ahi hi.
Matt. 5:11 ¶ “Keima hanga zahkona, bawlsiatna, a man lopi a mawhsakna namkim note in na thuak uh ciangin mi hampha na hi uh hi.
Matt. 5:12 Vantung ah thaman lianpi sang ding na hih manun kipak unla lungdam mahmah un. Note ma a kamsangte zong tua bangin a bawlsia zo uh hi.
Matt. 5:13 ¶ “Note in leitung mite aa dingin ci na hi uh hi. Ahih hangin ci pen al nawn keileh bangci bangin ki-alkiksak thei ding ahi hiam? Paikhia a mite tuatcil gawp ding longal a kimanna om lo hi.
Matt. 5:14 ¶ “Note in leitung mite aa dingin khuavak na hi uh hi. Mual dawna om khua kiliah thei lo hi.
Matt. 5:15 Kuamah in mei a vak khit ciangin seeng a khuh ngei kei hi. Inn sunga om mi khempeuh in khuavak a ngah theih nadingin meivak tunna tungah meivak a koih zaw uh hi.
Matt. 5:16 Tua mah bangin mite in note gamtat phate mu a, vana om na Pa uh a phat theih nadingun mite mai ah na khuavak uh na taangsak un.
Matt. 5:17 ¶ “Thukham ahi a, Kamsangte laibute ahi zongin a beisak dinga hong pai hong sa kei un. A beisak dinga hong pai hi loin a kicingsak dinga hong pai ka hi zaw hi.
Matt. 5:18 ¶ “Note kiang a man takpi kong cihin ah, van le lei a mangthang zongin thukham khempeuh a tangtun khit mateng laimal neupen khat ahi a, laimal them khat nangawn ahi zongin a mangthang kei ding hi.
Matt. 5:19 Tua ahih manin thupiakte lak panin a neupen khat nangawn palsat a, midangte zong a palsat dinga a hilh mi peuhmah vantung kumpigam sungah a neupen kici ding hi. Ahi zongin hih thupiaknate zui in midangte zong a zui dingin a hilh mi peuhmah vantung kumpigam sungah milian a kici ding hi.
Matt. 5:20 Tua hi a, ken kong cih in ah note dikna in thukhamhilh siate le Pharisee pawlte dikna a khup zawh keileh vantung kumpigam sungah na lut thei kei ding uh hi.
Matt. 5:21 ¶ “~ ‘Mi na that kei ding hi. Mi thatte in thukhenna thuak ding uh hi,’ ci a, tanglai mite tunga a kigen thu na za zo uh hi.
Matt. 5:22 Ahih hangin note kiang ken kong cih in ah a sanggampa tungah a thu om lopi a a heh mi peuhmah in thukhenna a thuak ding lauhuai hi. A sanggampa kiangah, ‘Nang, mi gina lo!’ a ci mi in zong thukhenna a thuak ding lauhuai hi. A sanggampa kiangah, ‘Nang, mi hai!’ a cite hell meikuang sungah a kikhul ding lauhuai hi.
Matt. 5:23 ¶ “ Biaknatauah Pasian biak nading nate tawi a na om laitakin na sanggampa nang tungah lungkim lo hi ci a, na phawk leh,
Matt. 5:24 Pasian na biak nading nate pen biaknatau mai ah koihphot in ciahkik inla, na sanggampa tawh va kilem masa in. Tua khit ciangin paikik inla Pasian na biakna nate piapan in.
Matt. 5:25 ¶ “Na langpa tawh thukhen zum zuana na pai laitakin kilem mengmeng in. Tua hi keileh amah in thukhenpa tungah hong khia in thukhenpa in palikte tungah hong ap ding a, palikte in thong sungah hong khum ding uh hi.
Matt. 5:26 ¶ “A man takpi kong cihin ah, na liausum dangka na piak khit matengin thong pan na suakta kei ding hi.
Matt. 5:27 ¶ “~ ‘Ang na kawm kei ding hi,’ ci a, tanglai mite tunga a kigen thu na za zo uh hi.
Matt. 5:28 Ahih hangin note kiang ken kong cih in ah mawh nopna lungsim tawh numei khat a en mi peuhmah, tua numei tungah a lungsim mawh zo hi.
Matt. 5:29 ¶ “Tua ahih manin na taklam mit in hong khialhsak leh khelkhia inla pai in; banghang hiam cihleh hell sungah na pumpi bupin hong kikhiat sangin na pumpi nate khat kisia leh a hoihzaw hi.
Matt. 5:30 Na taklam khut in hong khialhsak leh sattan inla pai in. Na pumpi bupin hell sungah hong kikhiat sangin na pumpi nate khat kisia leh a hoihzaw hi.
Matt. 5:31 ¶ “Tua banah, ‘A zi a ma nuam mi peuhmah in, a zi tungah kimakna lai pia tahen,’ a cihna thu na thei zo uh hi.
Matt. 5:32 Ahih hangin note kiang ken kong cih in ah mi khatpeuh in pasal dang tawh a mawhna longal thu dang khatpeuh hangin a zi a mak leh, a zi mi dang tawh a mawh dingin a bawl ahi hi. A kimasa numei a teenpih mi peuhmah zong mi zi tawh a mawh ahi hi.
Matt. 5:33 ¶ “Tua banah, ‘A man lopi in na kiciam kei ding a, ahi zongin Topa tunga na kamciamte tangtungsak in,’ ci in tanglai mite tunga a kigen thu na thei zo uh hi.
Matt. 5:34 Ahih hangin note kiang ken kong cih in ah na kiciam peuhmah kei un. Vantung in Pasian tokhom ahih manin vantung tawh kiciam kei un.
Matt. 5:35 Leitung in ama khengakna ahih manin leitung tawh kiciam kei un. A lian Kumpipa khuapi ahi Jerusalem min tawh kiciam kei un.
Matt. 5:36 Na lutang uh tawh zong kiciam kei in; banghang hiam cihleh na samzang khat na kangsak, na vomsak thei kei hi.
Matt. 5:37 Ahi thute, ‘Hi mah hi,’ ci unla, a hi lo thute, ‘Hi lo hi,’ ci un. Hih zah val in a tam zawk leh gilopa kiang panin a hong piang ahi hi.
Matt. 5:38 ¶ “~ ‘Mit tang khat tangin mit tang khat, ha tang khat tangin ha tang khat,’ a cihna thu na za zo uh hi.
Matt. 5:39 Ahih hangin ken kong cih in ah mi gilopa na dokik kei un. Mi khatpeuh in na pang taklam hong bet leh a langkhat zong na dawh in.
Matt. 5:40 Mi khatpeuh in na puanak hong suh nop manin zum ah hong khiat sawm leh na puan tungsilh zong na piak beh in.
Matt. 5:41 Zawhthawhthu tawh tai khat hong paipih nuamte, tai nih dong na zui in.
Matt. 5:42 Hong ngente na pia in. Hong leitawi nuamte na nungngat kei in.
Matt. 5:43 ¶ “~ ‘Na vengte it inla, na galte mudah in,’ cih thu na za zo uh hi.
Matt. 5:44 Ahi zongin ken kong cih in ah na galte na it un. Hong samsiate thupha na pia un. Hong mudahte tungah thupha na bawl un. A hong simmawh mite le hong bawlsia mite aa dingin thu na ngetsak un.
Matt. 5:45 Tua hi leh vana om na Pa uh tate na hi taktak ding uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh amah in mi hoih lote le mi hoihte tungah a kibangin ama ni suaksak a, mi dikte le mi dik lote tungah guah zong a zusak tuak hi.
Matt. 5:46 Hong itte bek it le uh teh, bang lemlawh tuam ding na hi uh hiam? Siahdongte nangawn in zong amau a itte it uh hi lo ahi hiam?
Matt. 5:47 Na lawmte bek maitai le uh teh, midangte sangin na hoih zawkna uh bang om tuan ding ahi hiam? Siahdongte nangawn in zong tua bangmah in hih uh hi lo ahi hiam?
Matt. 5:48 Tua ahih ciangin vana om na Pa uh a hoihkim bangin note zong na hoihkim un,” a ci hi.
Matt. 6:1 ¶ “Na hoih na sep uh ciangin mite muh theih theih dingin na hih khak loh nadingun kidawm un. Tua hi keileh vantung a om na Pa un thaman a hong pia kei ding hi.
Matt. 6:2 ¶ “Tua ahih manin a kitangsam mite huhna na piak uh ciangin a kineihkhem mite piak bangin pia kei un. Amaute in midangte pahtak ding lametna tawh kongzing lak le kikhopna innte ah pengkul tumkawmsa in a pia uh hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, amaute in thaman a ngah zo uh hi.
Matt. 6:3 Ahi zongin note in a kitangsam mite huhna na piak uh ciangin na taklam khut tawh na piakte uh na veilam khut theisak kei un.
Matt. 6:4 Tua hi leh a kitangsam mite na huhnate uh kilangkhia lo dinga a kilang lote a mu na Pa un a kilangtang in thaman hong pia ding hi.
Matt. 6:5 ¶ “Thu na nget uh ciangin zong a kineihkhem mite hih bangin hih kei un. Amaute in mite muh theih theih dingin kikhopna innte le lamkabom khawng ah ding a, thunget ding a ut uh hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, amaute in thaman a ngah zo uh hi.
Matt. 6:6 Note in thu na nget uh ciangin inndei sungah lut unla kong na khak khit uh ciangin a kilang lo a om na Pa uh kiangah ngen un. Tua hi leh a kilang lote a mu na Pa un a kilangtang in thaman hong pia ding hi.
Matt. 6:7 Thu na nget uh ciangin lawkite bangin na gen sasa uh gen phapha kei un. Amaute in gen pha kikkik le uh a ngahdeuh ding kisa uh hi.
Matt. 6:8 Tua ahih manin amaute bang hi kei un; banghang hiam cihleh na Pa un na kisapnate uh na nget ma un a thei khinzo hi.
Matt. 6:9 ¶ “Tua ahih manin hih bangin thu na ngen un, Vantung a om kote Pa aw, Na min siangtho kizahtak hen.
Matt. 6:10 Na kumpigam hong piang tahen. Vantung ah na deihna a kisep mah bangin, Leitung ah zong kisem tahen.
Matt. 6:11 Tuni a ka nek ding uh an hong pia in.
Matt. 6:12 Ko tunga hong khialte ka maisak uh bangin, Kote khialhna zong hong maisak ta in.
Matt. 6:13 Ze-etna sungah hong lutsak kei inla, Gilopa kiang panin hong honkhia in. Banghang hiam cihleh ukzawhna, Vangliatna le minthanna, Nang aa ahi tawntung hi. Amen.
Matt. 6:14 ¶ “Mite khialhnate na maisak uh leh vantunga om na Pa un zong note khialhnate hong maisak ding hi.
Matt. 6:15 Mite khialhnate na maisak kei uh leh na Pa un zong note khialhna hong maisak lo ding hi.
Matt. 6:16 ¶ “Tua banah an na tan uh ciangin, a kineihkhem mite bangin na mai uh vulsak kei un; banghang hiam cihleh amaute in antang ahihna uh mite mai ah a kilat theih nadingin a maipuak uh a khel uh hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, amaute in thaman a ngah zo uh hi.
Matt. 6:17 Ahi zongin note in an na tan uh ciangin na lu uh sathau nilh unla na mai uh phiat un.
Matt. 6:18 Tua hi leh na antan lam uh mite mai ah kilang lo ding a, a kilang lo a om na Pa uh mai bekah a kilang ding hi. Tua ciangin a kilang lote a mu na Pa un a kilangtang in thaman a hong pia ding hi.
Matt. 6:19 ¶ “Na sum na paite uh nget in a nek theihna, a kekseu theihna le gutate in luh in a guk theihna hih leitung ah khol kei un.
Matt. 6:20 Nget in a nek theih lohna, a kekseu theih lohna, gutate in luhin a guk theih lohna vantung ah khol zaw un.
Matt. 6:21 Banghang hiam cihleh na sum omna munah na lungsim uh zong a om ding hi.
Matt. 6:22 ¶ “Mittang in pumpi aa dingin meivak ahi hi. Tua ahih manin na mit a ciim leh na pumpi bup a vak ding hi.
Matt. 6:23 Ahih hangin na mit a mial leh na pumpi bup a mial ding hi. Tua ahih manin na sunga om khuavak pen khuamial hi leh a nak mial mahmah ding hi.
Matt. 6:24 ¶ “Kuamah in to nih na semkhawm thei lo hi; banghang hiam cihleh khat mudah in khat a it ding hi. Ahih keileh khat thupi simin khat a simmawh ding hi. Pasian na le leitung na na semkhawm thei kei ding uh hi.
Matt. 6:25 ¶ “Tua ahih manin note kianga kong cihin ah, bang ne in bang dawn ding ka hi hiam ci in na nuntakna aa dingun lunghimawh kei un. Bang silh in bang teeng ding ka hi hiam ci in na pumpi aa dingun lunghimawh kei un. Nek le tak sangin nuntakna thupi zaw a, silh le teen sangin pumpi thupi zaw hi lo ahi hiam?
Matt. 6:26 Vana leng vasate en dih un. Amaute in khaici tuh loin, an la lo uh a, bem le salah zong an a khol kei uh hi. Ahi zongin, vantunga om na Pa un amaute an a vak hi. Vasate sangin manpha zaw hi lo na hi uh hiam?
Matt. 6:27 Na lunghimawh manun na tun uh tong khat nangawn a behlap thei kua om na hi uh hiam?
Matt. 6:28 ¶ “Tua ahih leh banghang in puansilh ding lunghimawh na hi uh hiam? Gamlak a unokpakte khankhiat zia ngaihsun dih un. Amaute in na sem loin khau zong khek lo uh hi.
Matt. 6:29 Ahih hangin ken kong cih in ah Solomon in a minthanna khempeuh tawh kizem a a om laitak nangawn in hih pakte khat zahin hoih zo nai lo uh hi.
Matt. 6:30 Upna neu mite aw, tuni in om a zingciang in meikhuk ah a kikhul ding gamlak a pakte nangawn Pasian in tua bangin puansilh guan ahih leh note hong limguat zawkan ding hi lo ahi hiam?
Matt. 6:31 Tua ahih manin, ‘Bang ka ne ding a, bang ka dawn ding hiam, bang silh dinga bang teeng ding ka hi hiam?’ ci in lunghimawh kei un.
Matt. 6:32 Gentilete in hih nate khempeuh a zonpi pen uh ahi hi. Vantunga om na Pa un hih na khempeuh na kisap lam uh hong thei hi.
Matt. 6:33 Tua ahih manin Pasian kumpigam le ama dikna zong masa un. Tua hi leh hih nate khempeuh hong kipiakthuah ding hi.
Matt. 6:34 Tua ahih manin zingciang aa dingin lunghimawh khol kei un; banghang hiam cihleh zingciang vai ding zingciang mahin hong lunghimawh ding hi. Tuni a lungkhamna pen tuni aa dingin kicing khin hi.
Matt. 7:1 ¶ “Thukhenna na thuak loh nadingun midangte tungah thu na khen kei un.
Matt. 7:2 Banghang hiam cihleh midangte tunga thu na khen bangun no tungah zong thu hong kikhen ding hi. Note zat tehna tektek mah tawh note aa dingin a hong kitehsakkik ding hi.
Matt. 7:3 ¶ “Nangma mita singluang phawk kha loin banghang in na sanggampa mita ninthem muhsak na hi hiam?
Matt. 7:4 Ngaihsun dih in na mit ah singluang khat om napi banghang in na sanggampa kiangah, ‘Na mita ninthem hong lakkhiatsak ning,’ ci thei na hi hiam?
Matt. 7:5 A kineihkhem mipa aw! Nangma mita singluang lakhia masa in. Tua hi leh na sanggampa mita ninthem telmuh in na lakkhiatsak thei pan ding hi.
Matt. 7:6 ¶ “A siangtho nate uite pia kei un. Kepsuangmanphate zong vokpi mai ah lot kha kei un. Na lot khak leh a khe tawh tuangawp in kihei in nang a hong petgawp ding hi.
Matt. 7:7 ¶ “Ngen un, hong kipia ding hi. Zong un, na mu ding uh hi. Kiu un, hong kihon ding hi.
Matt. 7:8 Banghang hiam cihleh a ngente in ngah a, a zongte in mu in, a kiute kong kihon ding hi.
Matt. 7:9 ¶ “Note lakah a ta in anlum ngen leh suang a pia ding,
Matt. 7:10 ngasa ngen leh gul a pia ding kua om na hi uh hiam?
Matt. 7:11 No mi hoih lote nangawn in na tate uh na hoih piak ding thei na hih uh leh vana om na Pa un ama kianga a ngente na hoih hong pia zaw tham lo ding ahi hiam!
Matt. 7:12 Tua ahih manin note tunga hong kibawl dinga na deih khempeuh uh midangte tungah zong na bawl un. Thukham le Kamsangte laibute zong hih thu mah ahi hi.
Matt. 7:13 ¶ “Kong kawcik ah lut un; banghang hiam cihleh siatna mun tun nading kongpi zai a, lampi zong tanzau ahih manin mi tampi in tua lampi a tawn uh hi.
Matt. 7:14 Nuntakna mun tun nading kong kawcik a, lampi zong neu ahih manin mi tawmcik bekin a zui uh hi.
Matt. 7:15 ¶ “A lungsim tawng uh ngia bangin gilo napi tuuvun silh a, note kianga a hong pai kamsang zuaute na kidawm un.
Matt. 7:16 Amaute bangci mi hiam cih a gah panun na thei ding uh hi. Lingkung panin lenggah kilo thei ahi hiam? Thangling kung panin theigah kilo thei ahi hiam?
Matt. 7:17 Tua ahih manin singkung hoih peuhmah in a gah hoih a, singkung hoih keileh a gah zong a hoih kei hi.
Matt. 7:18 Singkung hoihin gah hoih lo gah thei lo a, singkung hoih loin gah hoih a gah thei kei hi.
Matt. 7:19 Gah hoih a gah lo singkung khempeuh kiphuk in meikuang sungah kikhul ding hi.
Matt. 7:20 Tua ahih manin amaute bangci mi hiam cih a gah panun na thei ding uh hi.
Matt. 7:21 ¶ “~‘Topa aw, Topa aw,’ hong ci peuhmah vantung kumpigam sungah a lutkim kei ding uh hi. Vana ka Pa deih banga a gamtate bek a lut ding uh hi.
Matt. 7:22 Tua ni ciangin mi tampi in, ‘Topa aw, Topa aw, nangma min tawh kamsang in thugen hi lo ka hi uh hiam? Nangma min tawh dawite hawlkhia in, nangma min tawh nalamdang bawl hi lo ka hi uh hiam?’ hong ci ding uh hi.
Matt. 7:23 Tua ciangin, ‘Note kong thei kei hi. Siatna a bawl mite aw, ka kiang panin paikhia un!’ ka ci ding hi.
Matt. 7:24 ¶ “Tua ahih manin hih ka thugente za a a zui mi khatpeuh in suangpi tunga innlam mi pilpa tawh kibang hi ci in ka gen ding hi.
Matt. 7:25 Guahzu in tui hong khang a, huihpi nungin tua inn a nawk hangin suangpi tungah kilam ahih manin a puk kei hi.
Matt. 7:26 Hih ka thugente za napi in a zui lo mi in, sehnel tunga innlam mi haipa tawh kibang hi ci in ka gen ding hi.
Matt. 7:27 Guahzu in tui hong khang a, huihpi nungin tua inn a nawk ciangin a puk hi. Tua pukna in a lian mahmah pukna ahi hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 7:28 ¶ Zeisu in hih thute a gen khit ciangin mi honpite in a thuhilhna lamdang a sa mahmah uh hi.
Matt. 7:29 Banghang hiam cihleh thukhamhilh siate bangin hilh loin thuneipa bangin a hilh hi.
Matt. 8:1 ¶ Zeisu mual tung pan hong kumsuk khit ciangin mi honpite in amah a zui uh hi.
Matt. 8:2 Tua ciangin, en in, miphak khat hong pai in amah bia a, “Topa aw, hong damsak nuam lecin nong damsak thei hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:3 ¶ Zeisu in a khut zanin amah lawng a, “Kong damsak nuam hi, damta in,” ci a, thu a piak ciangin thakhatin a dam pah hi.
Matt. 8:4 Tua ciangin Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Hih thu kuama kiangah gen kei in. Ahi zongin pai inla siampipa kiangah va kilak in. Amaute tungah teci ahi dingin Moses hong thupiakna bangin biakpiakna khat va pia in,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:5 ¶ Capernaum khua ah Zeisu a lut ciangin galkap 100 ukpa khat hong pai in thum a,
Matt. 8:6 “Topa aw, ka inn ah ka nasempa a pumzaw in lumcip a, genthei mahmah hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:7 ¶ Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Hong pai in amah ka damsak ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:8 ¶ Tua ciangin galkap 100 ukpa in dawngkik a, “Topa aw, ka inn sunga nong lut ding ka kilawm kei hi. Thu pia ziau leteh ka nasempa a dam ding hi.
Matt. 8:9 Banghang hiam cihleh kei zong mi khutnuai a om khat ka hi a, ka khutnuai ah zong galkapte a om uh hi. Amaute khat kiangah, ‘Pai in,’ ka cih ciangin pai a, a dang khat kiangah, ‘Hong pai in,’ ka cih ciangin a hong pai hi. Ka nasempa kiangah, ‘Hih sem in,’ ka cih ciangin a sem hi,” a cisak hi.
Matt. 8:10 ¶ Zeisu in tua thu a zak ciangin lamdangsa mahmah a, amah a zui mite kiangah, “Note kiang ken kong cih in ah Israelte sung nangawn ah hi zah a a lian upna ka mu kei hi!
Matt. 8:11 Ken kong cih in ah nisuahna le nitumna lam panin mi tampi hong pai in Abraham, Isaac le Jacobte tawh vantung kumpigam sungah a tukhawm ding uh hi.
Matt. 8:12 Ahi zongin tua kumpigam tate ahih leh a pualam khuamial lakah a lawnkhia ding hi. Tua munah kahna leh hagawina a om ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:13 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in galkap 100 ukpa kiangah, “Ciahkik in. Na upna bangin nang aa dingin piang tahen,” a ci hi. Tua hun lian mahin a nasempa a dam hi.
Matt. 8:14 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Peter inn ah Zeisu hong hawh in Peter sunghnu nattun in lupna tunga lum a mu hi.
Matt. 8:15 Amah in tua nu khut a lawn ciangin a natna dam a, tho in amaute zin a do pah hi.
Matt. 8:16 ¶ Nitak lam ciangin dawilut mi tampi Zeisu kiangah hong paipih uh a, tua dawite kam khat pauna bek tawh a hawlkhia ziau hi. Cina khempeuh zong a damsak hi.
Matt. 8:17 Hih thu pen kamsangpa Isaiah in, “Amah in i zawngkhalna teng lakhia in, i cinatna teng a pua hi,” ci a, a gensa thu a tangtunna ahi hi.
Matt. 8:18 ¶ Zeisu in ama kima om mi honpite a muh ciangin galkhat lamah galkah dingin a nungzuite thu a pia hi.
Matt. 8:19 Tua laitakin thukhamhilh siate khat ama kiangah hong pai a, “Sia aw, na paina peuhah kong zui ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:20 ¶ Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Ngiate in kua nei uh a, vana leng vasate in zong bu a nei uh hi. Ahih hangin Mihing Tapa in a lutang ngakh nading mun a nei kei hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:21 ¶ Tua khit ciangin ama nungzuite khat in, “Topa aw, ka pa vui dingin hong paisak masa phot in,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:22 ¶ Ahih hangin Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Hong zui in. Misi pen misite mahin na vui uh hen,” a ci hi.
Matt. 8:23 ¶ Gunkuang sungah amah a kahtoh ciangin a nungzuite in zong a zui uh hi.
Matt. 8:24 Tua ciangin tuilipi tungah thakhatin huih khauh mahmah hong nung a, tuihual in gunkuang a tum dekdek hi. Zeisu ahih leh a ihmu hi.
Matt. 8:25 A nungzuite ama kiangah pai in phong uh a, “Topa aw, a simang khin ding ka hita uh hi, hong hon in!” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 8:26 ¶ Zeisu in, “Upna neu mite aw, banghang in hi zahtakin lau zawzen na hi uh hiam?” a cih khit ciangin tho a, huihpi le tuihual a taii leh a dai pah hi.
Matt. 8:27 ¶ Amaute in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Hihpa bangci bang mi hi zawzen ahi hiam? Huihpi le tuihualte nangawn in ama thu a mang tazen uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 8:28 ¶ Zeisu tuilipi galkhat a om Gergesa mite teenna kuam a tun ciangin dawilut mi nih han pan hong paikhia uh a, amah a na dawntuah uh hi. Amaute gilo in gamhtat mahmah uh ahih manin kuamah in tua lampi a tawn ngam kei uh hi.
Matt. 8:29 Amaute thakhatin awng uh a, “Pasian Tapa Zeisu aw, nang tawh ka kisaina uh bang om ahi hiam? A hun tung nai lopi in kote bawlsia dinga hong pai na hi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 8:30 ¶ Amaute tawh a kigamla simsim ah vok honpi gamta in a om hi.
Matt. 8:31 Dawite in ama kiangah, “Nong hawlkhiat leh hualai a vok honte sungah hong lutsak in,” ci in a thum uh hi.
Matt. 8:32 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Pai un,” ci in thupia a, tua dawite paikhia in vok honte sungah a lut uh hi. Thakhat thu mahin vok hon khempeuh ken lakah taiphialsuk uh a, tuilipi sung kidenna in a si khin uh hi.
Matt. 8:33 Vok cingte tai pah vingveng uh a, dawilut mite tunga thupiang khempeuh khua sungah a va gen uh hi.
Matt. 8:34 ¶ Tua ciangin tua khua mite a khuazang un Zeisu en dingin hong paikhia uh a, a muh uh ciangin amau gam panin a paikhiat nading a ngen uh hi.
Matt. 9:1 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu gunkuang tuangin galkah a, ama khua a tung hi.
Matt. 9:2 Tua leh, en in, pumzaw mi khat a lupna tawh zawngin ama kiangah hong paipih uh hi. Zeisu in amaute upna a muh ciangin pumzawpa kiangah, “Ka ta aw, lungnuam in na mawhnate hong kimaisak zo hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 9:3 ¶ Tua thu a zak phetun thukhamhilh siate pawlkhat in a lungsim uhah, “Hihpa Pasian tungah a pausia hi!” a ci pah uh hi.
Matt. 9:4 ¶ Zeisu in amaute ngaihsutna thei ahih manin, “Banghang in note lungsim sungah thusia ngaihsun na hi uh hiam?
Matt. 9:5 ‘Na mawhnate hong kimaisak zo hi,’ cih ding le, ‘Tho inla lampai in,’ cih ding koi baih zaw ahi hiam?
Matt. 9:6 Ahi zongin Mihing Tapa in leitung ah mawhmaisak theihna thuneihna a neih lam na theih nadingun,” a cih khit ciangin pumzawpa kiangah, “Tho in, na lupna pua inla, na inn ah ciah in,” a ci hi.
Matt. 9:7 Tua pa zong tho in a inn ah a ciah hi.
Matt. 9:8 ¶ Mi honpite in hih thupiang a muh uh ciangin, lamdangsa mahmah uh a, mihingte tungah tua bang vangliatna a pia Pasian a phat uh hi.
Matt. 9:9 ¶ Tua mun panin Zeisu paisuak a, siahdonna buuk sunga a tu Matthew kici mi khat a muh ciangin, “Hong zui in,” a ci hi. Matthew zong dingkhia in Zeisu a zui hi.
Matt. 9:10 ¶ Inn sungah Zeisu an ne in a tut laitak, en in, siahdongte le mawhneite tampitak hong pai in Zeisu le a nungzuite tawh ankuang a umkhawm uh hi.
Matt. 9:11 Pharisee pawlte in a muh uh ciangin a nungzuite kiangah, “Banghang in na siapa un siahdongte le mawhneite tawh an nekhawm ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 9:12 ¶ Tua thu a zak ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Cidamte aa dingin siavuan kisam lo a, cinate aa ding bekin kisam hi.
Matt. 9:13 Ahih hangin va pai unla, ‘Gangawh biakna sangin hehpihna ka deih zaw hi,’ a cihna thu a khiatna va kantel phot un; banghang hiam cihleh mi dikte sam dinga hong pai ka hi kei hi. Mawhneite a kisikkik theih nadingun a sam dinga hong pai ka hi hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 9:14 ¶ Tua khit ciangin John nungzuite a kiangah hong pai uh a, “Kote le Phariseete in an ka tang zelzel uh hi; banghang in na nungzuite in antang lo uh ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 9:15 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Zineipa tawh a omkhop sungun a lawm a gualte thum le tau in ombuang ding uh ahi hiam? Ahih hangin amaute kiang pan zineipa a kilakkhiat hun hong tung ding a, tua ciangin bel an a tang ding uh hi.
Matt. 9:16 ¶ “Puan lui a kiphop ciangin kuamah in a ton nai lo puanbek a thak tawh a phop kei hi. Tua bangin phop leh a phopna puanbek a thak in puan lui kaikek in, a kekna a zai semsem ding hi.
Matt. 9:17 Kuamah in savun um lui sungah lenggahzu thak a thun kei hi. Tua bangin kithun leh savun um puakkham in lenggahzu teng luangkhia ding a, savun um zong a kisia ding hi. Lenggahzu thakte savun um thak sung mahah a kithun hi. Tua hi leh a nih tuakin bitkhawm in sawtveipi kikoih thei hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 9:18 ¶ Hih thute a gengen laitakin, en in, makaipa khat hong pai in amah bia a, “Ka tanu tu mahmahin a si hi. Ahi zongin nang hong pai in a tungah na khut nga leteh a hing ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 9:19 Zeisu dingkhia in amah zui a, a nungzuite in zong a zui uh hi.
Matt. 9:20 ¶ Tua laitakin kum sawm le kum nih sung siluang natna a vei numei khat in Zeisu nung lam pan zuanin a puanmongtep thakhatin a va lawng hi.
Matt. 9:21 Amah in a lungsim sungah, “A puan va lawng beek leng zong ka dam ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 9:22 ¶ Zeisu a nung lam ah kihei a, amah a muh ciangin, “Ka tanu aw, lungnuam in, na upna in hong damsak zo hi,” a ci hi. Tua hun lian mahin tua numei a dam hi.
Matt. 9:23 ¶ Makaipa inn sungah Zeisu a lut ciangin tamngai tumte le kap a gamlum ngeingai mi honpi a mu hi.
Matt. 9:24 Tua ciangin amah in tua mite kiangah, “Na awn un. Numeino a si hi loin a ihmu ahi hi,” a cih leh amaute in zahpihin a nuihsan uh hi.
Matt. 9:25 Ahih hangin Zeisu in mi honpi a pusuahsak khit ciangin inn sungah lut a, numeino khut a let ciangin numeino a tho hi.
Matt. 9:26 Hih thu tua gam mun khempeuh ah a kizel hi.
Matt. 9:27 ¶ Tua mun pan Zeisu a paikhiat ciangin, mittaw nih in amah zui uh a, “David Tapa aw, kote hong hehpih in!” ci in a kiko uh hi.
Matt. 9:28 ¶ Inn sungah amah a lut ciangin, mittaw nihte in zong a zui uh hi. Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Na mit uh a vaksak thei dingin nong um uh hiam?” ci in dong a, amaute in, “Kong um uh hi Topa aw,” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 9:29 ¶ Tua ciangin amah in a mit uh lawnsak a, “Na upna bangun, note tungah hong piang tahen,” a cih leh,
Matt. 9:30 a mit uh kihong pah hi. Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Hih thu kuamah theisak peuhmah kei un,” ci in khauhtakin thu a pia hi.
Matt. 9:31 Ahih hangin amaute paikhia uh a, tua gam sung khempeuh ah ama thu a kizelsak uh hi.
Matt. 9:32 ¶ Tua mi nihte a paikhiat laitak mah un, en in, a pauthei lo dawilut mi khat ama kiangah hong paipih uh hi.
Matt. 9:33 Amah in dawi a hawlkhiat ciangin, a pauthei lo pa hong pauthei pah hi. Mi honpi in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Israelte lakah hih bang i mu ngei kei hi!” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 9:34 ¶ Ahih hangin, Phariseete in, “Amah in dawi mangpipa min suangin dawite a hawlkhia ahi hi,” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 9:35 ¶ Tua bangin khuapi khuata kici tengah Zeisu zin kawikawi in amaute kikhopna innte ah thu a hilh hi. Kumpigam lungdamna thu tangko in cina le natna tuamtuam a nei mi khempeuh a damsak hi.
Matt. 9:36 Amah in mi honpite a et ciangin hehpihhuai a sa mahmah hi; banghang hiam cihleh amaute a cing om lo, a thabei, a kithehthang zelzul tuute tawh kibang uh hi.
Matt. 9:37 Tua hi a, a nungzuite kiangah, “An lak ding tam mahmah napi nasemte a tawm hi.
Matt. 9:38 Tua ahih manin an la ding nasemte hong sawl nadingin an nei Topa kiangah ngen un,” a ci hi.
