Matt. 17:20 ¶ Zeisu in, “Na up loh man uh ahi hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, ankamtang cia upna nei le uh teh, ‘Hih mualpi kiangah hih mun panin hualai ah va kikhinkhia in,’ ci le uh teh zong kikhinkhia ding hi. Note aa dingin a piang thei lo bangmah a om kei ding hi.
