Matt. 17:25 Peter in, “Pia mah hi,” a ci hi. ¶ Inn sungah Peter a lut phetin Zeisu in na hopih masa a, “Simon aw, bang na ci ngaihsut hiam? Leitung kumpite in mangmu ahi a, mimal siah ahi zongin a don uh ciangin a tate uh tung pan dong uh ahi hiam ahih keileh midangte tung pan dong zaw uh ahi hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
