Matt. 24:6 Gal kidona thu le gal hong tung ding hi cih thuthangte na za ding uh hi. Tua ciangin patau kei un; banghang hiam cihleh hih thu khempeuh a pian loh a phamawh hi a, ahi zongin beina a tung nai kei ding hi.
Matt. 24:7 Minam khat le minam khat, kumpigam khat le kumpigam khat hong kido ding uh hi. Kialpi le pulnatnate hong tung ding hi. Mun tuamtuam ah zin hong ling ding hi.
Matt. 24:8 Hihte khempeuh in nausuah kuana natna tawh a kibang haksatna kipatna ahi hi.
Matt. 24:9 ¶ “Tua ciangin bawlsiatna thuak dingin note hong ap ding uh a, hong that ding uh hi. Keima min hangin minam khempeuh in note hong mudah ding uh hi.
Matt. 24:10 Tua ciangin mi tampi lungkia ding uh a, khat le khat kilehhek in a kimudah ding uh hi.
Matt. 24:11 Kamsang zuau tampi hong piang ding a, mi tampi a khem ding uh hi.
Matt. 24:12 Siatna hong khang ding a, mi tampi in ki-itna a nei nawn kei ding uh hi.
Matt. 24:13 Ahi zongin a tawp donga a kipte in hotkhiatna a ngah ding uh hi.
Matt. 24:14 Minam khempeuh tungah teci ahi dingin Pasian kumpigam lungdamna thu leitung khempeuh ah kitangko ding a, tua khit ciangin beina a tung ding hi.
Matt. 24:15 ¶ “Kamsangpa Daniel in a lipkhaphuai siatna thu tawh kisai gen khin hi. Tua mipa in biakinnpi a siangtho mun ah a din hun na muh uh ciangin (a sim mi in thei tahen),
Matt. 24:16 Judea gam a om mite mual tung ah tai uh hen.
Matt. 24:17 Innkhum zanga om mi in na khatpeuh a la dingin inn sungah kumsuk kei hen.
Matt. 24:18 Lokuante zong puan la dingin inn ah ciahkik kei uh hen.
Matt. 24:19 Tua hun ciangin naupaite le nawine lai naungek a nei nupite a genthei mahmah ding uh hi!
Matt. 24:20 Na tai hun uh phalbi laitak le Sabbath ni ahih khak loh nadingin thungen un.
Matt. 24:21 Banghang hiam cihleh leitung piancil a kipan tudong in a piang ngei nai lo tunung ciangin zong a piang ngei nawn lo ding gimna lianpi tua hun ciangin a piang ding hi.
Matt. 24:22 Pasian in tua nite a tomsak keileh kuamah a suakta zo kei ding hi. Ahih hangin a teelsa mite a khualna in tua nite a tomsak ding hi.
Matt. 24:23 Tua hun ciangin mi khatpeuh in, ‘En in, hihlai ah Khazih om hi. Hualai ah Khazih om hi,’ hong cih uh hangin um kei un.
Matt. 24:24 Banghang hiam cihleh Khazih manlote le kamsang zuaute hong piang ding hi. Amaute in hi thei hi leh a teelsa mite nangawn a khem zawh nadingun lim lamdang le nalamdang lianpite a piangsak ding uh hi.
Matt. 24:25 En un, a hun hong tun ma in kong genkhol zo hi.
Matt. 24:26 ¶ “Amaute in, ‘En un, amah gamlak ah om hi!’ hong cih uh hangin zui kei un. ‘En un, amah inndeite sungah om hi!’ hong cih uh hangin um kei un.
Matt. 24:27 Banghang hiam cihleh nisuahna lam panin khua hong phia a, nitumna dong a tansuak bangin Mihing Tapa hong pai ciangin tua bangin a piang ding hi.
Matt. 24:28 Misi luang omna peuhah musanete a kikhawm ding uh hi.
Matt. 24:29 ¶ “Tua gimna lianpi hun a bei khit phetin, ni hong mial ding a, kha a tang nawn kei ding hi. Van panin aksite hong kia ding a, vantung vangliatnate kiling ding hi.
Matt. 24:30 ¶ “Tua laitakin vantung ah Mihing Tapa tawh kisai limlamdang hong kilang ding a, leitung minam khempeuh a kap ding uh hi. Mihing Tapa vantung panin vangliatna le minthanna lianpi tawh meii tung tuanga hong pai a mu ding uh hi.
Matt. 24:31 Amah in a ngaih mahmah pengkul aw tawh ama vantungmite sawl ding a, amaute in lei kiuli le van mong khat pan mong khat donga om a teelsa mite a kaikhawm ding hi.
Matt. 24:32 ¶ “Tu in theikung tawh kong gentehna panin hih thu na thei un. Theikung a hiangte meng a, a tehte hong sel ciangin khuakhal hong nai ta hi ci in na thei uh hi.
Matt. 24:33 Tua mah bangin hih thu khempeuh hong piang na muh uh ciangin tua hun nai mahmah ta a, kongbiang dong hong tung ta hi ci in na thei un.
Matt. 24:34 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, tulai khang mite a bei ma teitei in hih thu khempeuh hong piang ding hi.
Matt. 24:35 Van le lei mangthang ding a, ahi zongin ka thute a mangthang peuhmah kei ding hi.
Matt. 24:36 ¶ “A ni le a nai ding kuamah in a thei kei hi. Vana om vantungmite in zong a thei kei uh hi. Ka Pa bekin a thei hi.
Matt. 24:37 Noah hun lai bangin Mihing Tapa hong pai ciangin zong tua bang hi ding hi.
Matt. 24:38 Tuiciin tun ma a mite in Noah tembaw sungah a lut ni ciangdong, zukham ankham, kipi kiteeng in a om uh hi.
Matt. 24:39 Tuiciin tunga amaute khempeuh a tupmang dongin khuaphawk loin a om uh hi. Mihing Tapa hong pai ciangin zong tua mah bangin a piang ding hi.
Matt. 24:40 Tua hun ciangin lokuan mi nih khat kila in khat kinusia ding hi.
Matt. 24:41 An sukhawm numei nih khat kila in khat kinusia ding hi.
Matt. 24:42 ¶ “Na Topa uh hong pai ding hun thei lo na hih manun kiging den un.
Matt. 24:43 Ahi zongin hih thu thei un. Inn neipa in gutapa pai ding hun theikhol hi leh pang gige in a inn a luhsak kei ding hi.
Matt. 24:44 Tua ahih ciangin na lamet loh laitakun Mihing Tapa hong pai ding ahih manin note zong kigingsa in om un.
Matt. 24:45 ¶ “Inn sung vai khempeuh hawm a, annek huna inn sung mite an manman in a pia dinga a topa in a koih, a muanhuai le a pil nasem kua ahi hiam?
Matt. 24:46 A topa hong tun ciangin tua banga om nasem a muh nasempa in mi hampha ahi hi.
Matt. 24:47 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, amah in a neihsa khempeuh tua nasempa a uksak ding hi.
Matt. 24:48 Ahih hangin a hoih lo nasempa in a lungsim sungah, ‘Ka topa hong zekai lai ding hi,’ ci in ngaihsun henla,
Matt. 24:49 a naseppih a lawmte satgawp in, zukhamte tawh nekhawm dawnkhawm in na om leh,
Matt. 24:50 a lamet loh ni le a theih loh kalin a topa hong tungvat ding hi.
Matt. 24:51 A topa in amah tumnih suahin a kineihkhem mite tawh a thuakkhawmsak ding hi. Tualai ah kahna le hagawina a om ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 25:1 ¶ “Tua banah, vantung kumpigam in zipipa dawn dinga a kuankhia meivak a tawi nungak siangtho sawmte tawh kibang hi.
Matt. 25:2 Tuate lakah ngate pil uh a, a dang ngate a hai uh hi.
Matt. 25:3 A hai ngate in meivak a ken uh hangin meitui a keng kei uh hi.
Matt. 25:4 A pil ngate in ahih leh meivak a ken mah bangun meitui zong thawl sungah a keng uh hi.
Matt. 25:5 Ahih hangin zipipa hong tung hak ahih manin amaute khempeuh lusu in a ihmu uh hi.
Matt. 25:6 ¶ “Zankim laitakin kikona aw khat hong ging a, ‘Ngai un, zipipa hong paikhia ta hi. Amah dawn dingin hong pai un,’ a ci hi.
Matt. 25:7 ¶ “Tua ciangin tua nungak siangthote a vekpi un tho in a meivak ciat uh vak dingin a kipan uh hi.
Matt. 25:8 A haite in a pilte kiangah, ‘Ka meitui uh bei ahih manin na meitui uh hong hawm un,’ a ci uh hi.
Matt. 25:9 ¶ “A pilte in, ‘Kong hawm zo kei ding uh hi. Ko aa ding le no aa ding kicing lo ding ahih manin meitui zuakte kiangah pai in va lei un,’ a ci uh hi.
Matt. 25:10 ¶ “Amaute meitui lei dingin a pai kal un zipipa hong tung hi. Kigingsa a om mite zipipa tawh mopawi bawlna sungah lutkhawm uh a, tua ciangin kong a kikhak hi.
Matt. 25:11 ¶ “Tua khit ciangin nungak siangtho dang teng hong tungkik uh a, ‘Topa aw, Topa aw, kong hong hon in,’ a ci uh hi.
Matt. 25:12 Ahih hangin amah in, ‘A man takpi kong cihin ah, note kong thei kei hi,’ a ci hi.
Matt. 25:13 ¶ “Tua ahih ciangin, Mihing Tapa hong pai ding a ni le a nai thei lo na hih manun kigingkhol tawntung un.
Matt. 25:14 ¶ “Vantung kumpigam in a nasemte sama a neihsa teng a ap khit ciangin khual gamlapi ah a zinkhia mipa tawh kibang hi.
Matt. 25:15 Amah in amaute siamna zui in khatpa talent nga, khatpa talent nih, a dang khatpa talent khat a piak khit ciangin a zinkhia hi.
Matt. 25:16 Talent nga a sangpa in a metbawl ciangin a met talent nga a ngah hi.
Matt. 25:17 Tua mah bangin talent nih a sangpa in zong a met talent nih a ngah hi.
Matt. 25:18 Ahih hangin talent khat a sangpa in lei to in a topa sum a phum hi.
Matt. 25:19 ¶ “Hun sawtpi khit ciangin tua nasemte topa hong ciah a, a sum sazian a sit hi.
Matt. 25:20 Talent nga a sangpa in a dang talent nga hong tawi a, ‘Topa aw, sum talent nga nong ap hi. En in, a met talent nga ka ngah hi,’ a ci hi.
Matt. 25:21 ¶ “A topa in, ‘Hoih mahmah hi. A muanhuai nasem hoihpa aw, a tawmno khat tungah citak na hih manin na tampi kong uksak ding hi. Na topa tawh hong lungdamkhawm in,’ a ci hi.
Matt. 25:22 ¶ “Talent nih a sangpa zong hong pai a, ‘Topa aw, sum talent nih nong ap hi. En in, a met talent nih ka ngah hi,’ a ci hi.
Matt. 25:23 ¶ “A topa in, ‘Hoih mahmah hi. A muanhuai nasem hoihpa aw, a tawmno khat tungah citak na hih manin na tampi kong uksak ding hi. Na topa tawh hong lungdamkhawm in,’ a ci hi.
Matt. 25:24 ¶ “Tua khit ciangin talent khat a sangpa hong pai a, ‘Topa aw, khaici na tuh lohna munah an na la a, khaici na theh lohna munah an a kaikhawm, migenhak na hih lam kong thei hi.
Matt. 25:25 Tua ahih manin kong kihta a, lei sungah na sum ka phum hi. En in, na sum hihlai ah a om hi,’ a ci hi.
Matt. 25:26 ¶ “A topa in dawng a, ‘A gilo le a thadah nasempa aw, khaici ka tuh lohna munah an la in, ka theh lohna munah an ka kaihkhop lam hong thei na hih leh,
Matt. 25:27 summet bawlte kiangah ka sum na ap beek leteh kong tun ciangin ka sum le a met ka ngahkhawm thei ding hi.
Matt. 25:28 ¶ “~‘Tua ahih ciangin ama tunga om talent khat la unla talent sawm a neipa pia un.
Matt. 25:29 Banghang hiam cihleh a neite kipiak beh ding a, kicingtakin a nei ding uh hi. A nei lote ahih leh a neih sunsun nangawn uh a kilakkhiatsak ding hi.
Matt. 25:30 Tua ahih manin kimanna a nei lo tua nasempa a pualam khuamial sungah paikhia un. Tualai ah kahna le hagawina om ding hi,’ a ci hi.
Matt. 25:31 ¶ “Mihing Tapa in a minthanna le ama vantungmi siangthote khempeuh tawh hong pai ciangin ama minthanna kumpi tokhom tungah hong tu ding hi.
Matt. 25:32 Tua ciangin ama mai ah minam khempeuh kikhawmsak ding a, tuucingpa in tuu le kel a khen bangin amaute a khen ding hi.
Matt. 25:33 Tuute a taklam ah kelte a veilam ah a koih ding hi.
Matt. 25:34 ¶ “Tua khit ciangin Kumpipa in a taklama omte kiangah, ‘Ka Pa thupha piakte aw, hong pai unla leitung piancil a kipan note aa dingin a kibawlkholsa kumpigam hong luah un.
Matt. 25:35 Banghang hiam cihleh ka gilkial lai in an nong pia uh hi. Ka dangtak lai in ka dawn ding tui nong pia uh a, khualzin mi ka hihlai in zin nong do uh hi.
Matt. 25:36 Puan nei lo a ka omlai in puansilh nong pia uh hi. Ka cinat lai in nong veh uh a, thong ka kiat lai in nong hawh uh hi,’ a ci ding hi.
Matt. 25:37 ¶ “Tua ciangin mi dikte in dawng a, ‘Topa aw, na gilkial lam cik in hong mu a, an hong pia ka hi uh hiam? Na dangtak lam cik in hong mu a, na dawn ding tui hong pia ka hi uh hiam?
Matt. 25:38 Khualzin mi na hih lam cik in hong mu a, zin hong do ka hi uh hiam? Puan na neih loh lam cik in hong mu a, puansilh hong pia ka hi uh hiam?
Matt. 25:39 Na cinat, na thongkiat cik in hong mu a, hong veh ka hi uh hiam?’ ci in a dawng ding uh hi.
Matt. 25:40 ¶ “Tua ciangin Kumpipa in, ‘A man takpi kong cihin ah, hih ka sanggamte a neupen khat tunga na bawl peuhmah uh kei tunga hong bawl na hi uh hi,’ ci in a dawng ding hi.
Matt. 25:41 ¶ “Tua khit ciangin a veilam a omte kiangah, ‘Samsiatna a ngah mite aw, ka kiang panin paikhia un. Dawimangpa le a pawlte aa dingin a kibawlkholsa, a kuang tawntung meilipi sungah pai un.
Matt. 25:42 Banghang hiam cihleh ka gilkial lai in an nong pia kei uh a, ka dangtak lai in dawn ding tui nong pia kei uh hi.
Matt. 25:43 Khualzin mi ka hihlai in zin nong do kei uh a, puan nei lo a ka omlai in puansilh nong pia kei uh hi. Ka cinat lai le thong ka kiat lai in zong nong veh kei uh hi,’ a ci ding hi.
Matt. 25:44 ¶ “Tua ciangin amaute in, ‘Topa aw, na gilkial lai, na dangtak lai, khualzin mi na hihlai, puan nei lo a na omlai, na cinat lai le na thongkiat laitak cik in hong mu a, hong don kha lo ka hi uh hiam?’ a ci ding uh hi.
Matt. 25:45 ¶ “Tua ciangin Kumpipa in, ‘A man takpi kong cihin ah, hih mite a neupen khat tungah na bawl loh khempeuh uh, kei tungah zong a hong bawl lo na hi uh hi,’ ci in a dawng ding hi.
Matt. 25:46 ¶ “Tua ciangin a tawntung gawtna a thuak dingin amaute paikhia ding uh a, mi dikte ahih leh nuntak tawntungna munah a pai ding uh hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:1 ¶ Zeisu in hih thute khempeuh a gen khit ciangin, a nungzuite kiangah,
Matt. 26:2 “Ni nih khit ciangin Paisan Pawi hong tung ding hi cih na thei uh hi. Tua ni ciangin khailup dingin Mihing Tapa a kipia ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:3 ¶ Tua ciangin siampi liante, thukhamhilh siate le Judah mite makaite, Siampi Ukpa Caiaphas inntual ah a kikhawm uh hi.
Matt. 26:4 Amaute in thukawi, thuzuau tawh Zeisu manin thah ding a sawm uh hi.
Matt. 26:5 Ahi zongin, “Mi honpi hong lungso kha ding uh ahih manin pawi hun sungin hih kei ni,” a kici uh hi.
Matt. 26:6 ¶ Tu in, Bethany khua a teeng Simon miphakpa a kici pa inn ah Zeisu an ne in a tut laitak,
Matt. 26:7 numei khat in a manpha mahmah sathau namtui suangkang thawl khat tawi in hong pai a, Zeisu lu tungah a buak hi.
Matt. 26:8 ¶ Ahih hangin a nungzuite in a muh uh ciangin lungkim lo uh a, “Banghang in hih sathau namtui tuaci thangbawl ahi hiam?
Matt. 26:9 Sum tampi tawh zuak in mi zawngte kipia zaw leh,” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 26:10 ¶ Ahih hangin Zeisu in tua thu a theih ciangin amaute kiangah, “Banghangin tua numeinu nawngkaisak na hi uh hiam? Amah in kei tungah nasep hoih khat hong bawl khin hi.
Matt. 26:11 Mi zawngte note tawh om den uh a, kei ka hih leh note tawh ka omkhawm den kei ding hi.
Matt. 26:12 Amah in ka pumpi hih sathau namtui hong buah pen a kivui ding ka pumpi hong puahkhol ahi hi.
Matt. 26:13 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, hih lungdamna thu a kitangkona leitung mun khempeuh ah hih numeinu a kiphawk nadingin kei tungah a hong bawlna zong a kigen ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:14 ¶ Tua khit ciangin sawm le nihte lakah Judas Iscariot kici pa siampi liante kiangah va pai a,
Matt. 26:15 “Note khut ah amah hong pia hi leng kei bang hong pia ding na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. Amaute in nguntang 30 piak dingin a kithukim uh hi.
Matt. 26:16 Tua huna kipanin Judas in Zeisu a lehhek nading hun hoih a zong hi.
Matt. 26:17 ¶ Silngo Sawhloh Anlum Pawi a kipat ni in nungzuite Zeisu kiangah hong pai uh a, “Paisan Pawi an na nek nading koilai ah hong bawlkholhsak le ung na ut hiam?” a ci uh hi.
Matt. 26:18 ¶ Amah in, “Khua sungah va pai unla, kong gensa mipa kiangah, ‘Siapa in, “Ka hun hong nai ta ahih manin ka nungzuite tawh na inn ah Paisan Pawi ka bawl ding hi,” ci hi,’ va ci un,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:19 ¶ Nungzuite in Zeisu cih bangin hih uh a, Paisan Pawi an a bawlkhol uh hi.
Matt. 26:20 ¶ Nitak hong tun ciangin sawm le nihte tawh Zeisu a tukhawm hi.
Matt. 26:21 Amaute in an a nek laitakun amah in, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, note lakah khat in kei nong lehhek ding uh hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:22 ¶ Amaute dah mahmah uh a, ama kiangah, “Topa aw, kei ka hi hiam?” ci in a dong ciat uh hi.
Matt. 26:23 ¶ Zeisu in dawng a, “Ankuang ka sawkkhoppih pa in kei hong lehhek ding hi.
Matt. 26:24 Lai Siangtho sungah ama thu a kigelhsa bangin Mihing Tapa a pai ding mah ahi hi. Ahi zongin Mihing Tapa a lehhekpa in gimna a thuak ding hi! Tua pa mihing in a piangkhia lo hivet leh ama aa dingin hoihzaw ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:25 ¶ Amah a lehhekpa Judas in, “ Rabbiaw, kei ka hi hiam?” a cih ciangin amah in, “Na cih bangin na hi hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:26 ¶ Amaute in an a nek laitakun, Zeisu in anlum la a, lungdam a koh khit ciangin balkham in, “La unla, ne un. Hih in ka pumpi ahi hi,” ci in nungzuite a pia hi.
Matt. 26:27 ¶ Hai zong la a, lungdam a koh khit ciangin, “Na vekpi un dawn un.
Matt. 26:28 Hih in mi tampi mawhna a mai nadinga a luangkhia, thuciamna thak ka sisan ahi hi.
Matt. 26:29 Note kong genin ah ka Pa kumpigam sungah note tawh lenggahzu a thak ka dawn ni matengin tu a kipan ka dawn nawn kei ding hi,” ci in a pia hi.
Matt. 26:30 ¶ Amaute in biakna la khat a sak khit uh ciangin Olive Mual zuanin a paikhia uh hi.
Matt. 26:31 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Tu zan ciangin keima hangin na vekpi un na puk ding uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh Lai Siangtho sungah, ‘Tuucingpa ka sat ding a, Tuu honte a kithehthang ding uh hi,’ ci in a kigelh hi.
Matt. 26:32 ¶ “Ahih hangin ka thawhkik khit ciangin Galilee gam ah note ma in ka na paikhol ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:33 ¶ Peter in, “Nangma hangin mi khempeuh a puk zongin kei ka puk ngei kei ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:34 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, tuzan aak a khuan ma in thumvei nong nial ding hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:35 ¶ Peter in, “Nang tawh sihkhawm nading ahi zongin kong nial peuhmah kei ding hi,” a ci hi. Nungzui khempeuh in zong tua bangin a ci ciat uh hi.
Matt. 26:36 ¶ Gethsemane kici mun khat ah Zeisu a tun ciangin a nungzuite kiangah, “Hua pam lamah thu ka va nget sungin hihlai ah na tu un,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:37 Amah in Peter le Zebedee tapa nihte tonpih a, nakpitak a dahna le lunggim hong kipan hi.
Matt. 26:38 Tua khit ciangin amaute kiangah, “A si zo ding zahin ka lungsim gim lua mahmah hi. Hihlai ah om unla kei hong ngak un,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:39 ¶ Amah a gamla zawdeuh ah pai in boksuk a, “Ka Pa aw, hih hai tawh ka kipelh theih ding leh hong kipelhsak in. Ahi zongin, kei deihna bang hi loin, nang deihna bang hi zaw tahen,” ci in thu a ngen hi.
Matt. 26:40 ¶ Nungzuite kiang a tun ciangin amaute ihmu a om a mu hi. Amah in Peter kiangah, “Nai khat sung nangawn hong ngak zo lo na hi uh hiam?
Matt. 26:41 Ze-etna sungah na lut khak loh nadingun thungenin kiging un. Lungsim a ut mahmah hangin pumpi a thanem hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:42 ¶ Tua ciangin a nihveina va paikhiakikin thungen a, “Pa aw, hih hai kei tawh kipelh thei lo a, ka dawn loh a phamawh ahih leh nangma deihna bang hi tahen,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:43 ¶ Amah hong paikik ciangin nungzuite hak zo mahmah lo uh ahih manin ihmu in a om uh a mukik hi.
Matt. 26:44 Tua ciangin amaute nusia in va paikhiakik a, a nget ngei teng mah a thumveina a va ngen leuleu hi.
Matt. 26:45 ¶ Tua khit ciangin a nungzuite kiangah hong pai a, “Note ihmu mu lai in, tawlnga lailai ding na hi uh hiam? En in, Mihing Tapa mawhneite khut sungah a kipiak ding hun hong tungta hi.
Matt. 26:46 Tho unla pai ni. En un, kei hong lehhekpa hong nai mahmah ta hi,” a ci hi.
Matt. 26:47 ¶ Tua banga a gengen laitakin sawm le nihte lakah khat ahi Judas in siampi liante le Judah mite makaite in a sawl mi honkhat hong tonpih a, tua mite in namsau le molhtumte a tawi uh hi.
Matt. 26:48 Amah a lehhekpa in mihonte kiangah, “Ka nap mipa amah ahi hi man pah un,” ci in a theihsakna lim ahi hi.
Matt. 26:49 ¶ Amah in thakhatin Zeisu kiang hong naih a, “Rabbi aw, na dam hiam!” ci in a nam hi.
Matt. 26:50 ¶ Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Lawm aw, bang hih dinga hong pai na hi hiam?” a ci hi. Tua khit ciangin mi honpi hong pai uh a, Zeisu man in a paipih uh hi.
Matt. 26:51 Tua ciangin Zeisu tawh a omkhawmte khat in thakhatin a namsau dokin Siampi Ukpa nasempa a sat leh a bil a satkhia hi.
Matt. 26:52 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in tua pa kiangah, “Na namsau a paai ah siatkik in. Namsau tawi peuhmah namsau mah tawh a si ding uh hi.
Matt. 26:53 Tu mahmahin ka Pa kiangah a ngen thei lo hong sa na hi uh hiam? Ngen leng vantungmi legion sawm le nih sanga a tamzaw hong pia pah ding hi.
Matt. 26:54 Tua bangin a ngen hi leng hih banga a piang dingin Lai Siangtho sunga kigensa thute koici tangtun thei ding ahi hiam?” a ci hi.
