Matt. 28:20 Note kong piaksa thu khempeuh a zuih nadingun hilh un. En un, hun a bei dongin note kong ompih tawntung ding hi,” a ci hi. Amen.Mark 1:1 ¶ Pasian Tapa Zeisu Khazih lungdamna thu a kipatna in hih bang ahi hi.
Mark 1:2 Kamsangte laibu sungah, “En in, nangma lampi a sialkhol dingin, Na mai ah ka kamtaipa ka sawl hi.
Mark 1:3 Gamlak a kikopa awging in, ‘Topa pai nading lam na sial unla, Ama lampite na tangsak un,’ a ci hi,” ci in a kigelh hi.
Mark 1:4 ¶ John in gamlak ah mite tuiphum a, mawh maisak nadingin kisikkikna thu tawh kisai tuiphumna thu a hilh hi.
Mark 1:5 Tua ciangin Jerusalem khua mite a kipan Judea gama om mi khempeuh ama kiangah hong pai in a mawhnate uh pulak uh a, John in Jordan Gun ah amaute a tuiphum hi.
Mark 1:6 Tu in John in kalaoh mul kigan puan silhin, savun kawnggak tawh a kawng gak a, kauphe le gamlak khuaizu tawh a kivak hi.
Mark 1:7 Amah in, “Kei sanga a vanglian zaw khat hong pai lai ding hi. Kunsuk a a khedapkhau sut ding nangawn in ka kilawm kei hi.
Mark 1:8 En in keimah in note tui ah kong phum a, ahih hangin amah in note Kha Siangtho tawh hong phum ding hi,” ci in a hilh hi.
Mark 1:9 ¶ Tua hun laitakin Galilee gam Nazareth khua panin Zeisu hong pai a, John in Jordan Gun sungah a tuiphum hi.
Mark 1:10 Tuisung pan a hong paikhiat phetin van kihong a, Kha in vakhu bangin ama tungah hong kumsuk John in a mu hi.
Mark 1:11 Tua ciangin van panin aw khat hong ging a, “Nangmah in hong lungdamsak mahmah ka it ka Tapa na hi hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 1:12 ¶ Tua khit phetin Kha in gamlak ah Zeisu a sawlkhia pah hi.
Mark 1:13 Gamlak ah ni 40 sung Zeisu omin Satan ze-etna thuak a, gamsate tawh a omkhawm hi. Tua khit ciangin vantungmite in amah a kem uh hi.
