Mark 1:20 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute a sam pah hi. Amaute in a cial uh nasemte le a pa uh Zebedee gunkuang sungah nusia in Zeisu nung a zui uh hi.
Mark 1:21 ¶ Tua khit ciangin amaute Capernaum khua ah pai uh a, Sabbath ni ciangin kikhopna inn ah Zeisu lut pahin thu a hilh hi.
Mark 1:22 Amah in thukhamhilh siate hilh bangin hilh loin thuneipa bangin hilh ahih manin a thuhilhna lamdang a sa mahmah uh hi.
