Mark 1:24 Amah kiko in, “Nazareth khua mi Zeisu aw, kote hong hi ci omsak lel in! Nang tawh bang kisai ka hi uh hiam? Kote a susia dinga hong pai na hi hiam? Kua na hi hiam cih kong thei uh a, Pasian mi Siangthopa na hi hi,” a ci hi.
