Mark 1:38 ¶ Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Thu ka hilh theih nadingin hih kima om khua dangdangte ah zong pai ni; banghang hiam cihleh hih na sem ding maha hong pai ka hi hi,” a ci hi.
