Mark 1:44 “Hih thu kuama kiangah gen peuhmah kei in. Ahi zongin, pai inla siampipa kiangah va kilak in. Damna ngah na hih manin Moses hong thupiak bangin biakna va pia in. Tua in amaute tungah teci a suak ding hi,” a ci hi.
