Mark 2:11 “Tho in, na lupna pua inla na inn ah ciahin kong ci hi,” ci in a sawl hi.
Mark 2:12 Tua pa thakhatin tho a, a lupna pua in amaute khempeuh muhin a paikhia hi. Tua mite khempeuh in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Hih bang mahmah khatvei beek i mu ngei kei hi!” ci in Pasian a phat uh hi.
Mark 2:13 ¶ Tua khit ciangin tuili gei ah Zeisu paikhiakik in ama kiangah mipi khempeuh hong kikhawm uh a, amah in amaute thu a hilh hi.
