Mark 2:15 ¶ Tu in, Levi inn ah an ne dingin Zeisu a tut laitakin, siahdongte le mawhneite tampitak in zong Zeisu le a nungzuite tawh ankuang a umkhawm uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh tualai ah tua bang mi tampi in amah a zui uh hi.
Mark 2:16 Pharisee pawlte le thukhamhilh siate in siahdongte le mawhneite tawh an nekhawm in a om Zeisu a muh uh ciangin a nungzuite kiangah, “Banghang in amah in siahdongte le mawhneite tawh an nekhawm ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
Mark 2:17 ¶ Zeisu in tua thu a zak ciangin amaute kiangah, “Cidamte in siavuan kisam lo uh a, cinate bekin kisam uh hi. Mi dikte sam dinga hong pai ka hi kei a, mawhneite a kisikkik nadingun a sam dingin hong pai ka hi hi,” a ci hi.
