Mark 3:4 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Sabbath ni in a pha bawlhuai hiam a sia bawlhuai hiam? Nuntakna khat hotkhiathuai hiam thahhuai hiam?” ci in a dong hi. Ahih hangin amaute pau loin a dai khipkhep uh hi.
Mark 3:5 ¶ Amaute lungkhauhna hangin Zeisu in heh le dah thuah a, a kim a pam teng a ban et khit ciangin tua mipa kiangah, “Na khut zan in,” ci in a sawl hi. ¶ Amah in a zan leh a langkhat lam mah bangin a dam hi.
