Mark 3:10 Banghang hiam cihleh amah in mi tampi damsak ahih manin cina luna a om zahzah amah lawng kha nuamin a kiphu gawp uh hi.
Mark 3:11 Dawigilote in amah a muh uh ciangin, a mai ah pukin, “Nang in Pasian Tapa na hi hi,” ci in a kiko uh hi.
Mark 3:12 Ahi zongin, Zeisu in ama thu kuamah a theihsak loh nading uh khauhtakin a kham hi.
Mark 3:13 ¶ Zeisu in mual tung ah kahto in ama mi deih teng sam a, amaute zong ama kiangah a hong pai uh hi.
Mark 3:14 Tua khit ciangin amah in amah tawh a omkhawm ding le thuhilh a a sawlkhiat theih ding mi sawm le nih a seh hi.
