Mark 3:18 Andrew, Philip, Bartholomew, Matthew, Thomas, Alphaeus tapa James, Thaddaeus, Minamveipa Simon le
Mark 3:19 amah a lehhekpa Judas Iscariot ahi uh hi.
Mark 3:20 ¶ Tua ciangin mi honpite khatvei hong kikhawmkik uh ahih manin amaute in an nangawn ne man lo uh hi.
