Mark 3:23 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute samin thugentehna tawh thu a hilhin ah, “ Satanin bangci bangin Satan hawlkhia thei ding ahi hiam?
Mark 3:24 Gam khat peuhmah kiphelkhap leh tua gam ding zo lo ding hi.
Mark 3:25 Innkuan khat a kiphelkhap leh zong tua innkuan ding zo lo ding hi.
Mark 3:26 Satan amah le amah kido in kiphelkhap leh ding zo lo dinga beimang ding hi.
Mark 3:27 Mi thahatpa hencip masa loin kuamah in ama inn sungah lutin a neihsate a laksak zo kei ding hi. Amah a kihencip khit ciang bekin a inn a kiluh zo pan ding hi.
Mark 3:28 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, mihingte mawhna khempeuh le Pasian tunga pausiatnate a kimaisak ding hi.
