Mark 3:30 ¶ “Ama sungah dawigilo lut hi,” ci in ngawh uh ahih manin amah in hih thugentehna tawh a hilh ahi hi.
Mark 3:31 ¶ Tua laitakin a nu le a sanggamte ama kiangah hong pai uh a, amah a sam ding mi sawlin inn pualam ah a ngak uh hi.
