Mark 3:33 ¶ Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Ka nu le ka sanggamte kua ahi uh hiam?” ci in a dawng hi.
Mark 3:34 ¶ Amah in a kianga tu mite gualet a, “En un, hih mite in ka nu le ka sanggamte ahi uh hi.
