Mark 4:1 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in tuili gei ah thu a hilhkik hi. Mi honpite ama kiangah hong kikhawm uh ahih manin tui tunga om gunkuang sungah a tu hi. Mipi khempeuh in tuili lam nga in leilak ah a om uh hi.
Mark 4:2 Amah in thugentehna tawh thu tampi a hilhin ah,
Mark 4:3 “Ngai un! Khaici vawhpa khat khaici vawh dingin a kuankhia hi.
Mark 4:4 Khaici a vawh ciangin khaici pawlkhat lam gei ah tu a, vana vasate hong lengin a nemang uh hi.
Mark 4:5 Pawlkhatte leitang a tam lohna mun suang tungah tu a, lei a dai hangin a po pah hi.
Mark 4:6 Ahih hangin zungkha zo lo ahih manin ni hong suakin nisa in a kat ciangin a keumang uh hi.
Mark 4:7 Khaici pawlkhatte ling lakah tu a, lingkungte hong khangin depgawp ahih manin a gah zo kei uh hi.
Mark 4:8 Ahi zongin khaici pawlkhatte leihoihna ah a tu hi. Tuate po in hong khang a, pawlkhatte a zah 30, pawlkhatte a zah 60, pawlkhatte a zah 100 a gah uh hi,” a ci hi.
