Mark 4:12 ¶ “Tua in, ‘Amaute in enen napi a muh theih loh nading, Ngaingai napi a tel theih loh nading uh ahi hi. Tua hi keileh amaute hong kihei kha ding uh a, A mawhnate uh kimaisak ding hi,’ a cih thu a tangtun nading ahi hi,” ci in a dawng hi.
Mark 4:13 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Note in hih thugentehna tel zo lo na hih uh leh thugentehna khempeuh koici tel zawh ding na hi uh hiam?
Mark 4:14 Khaici vawhpa in Pasian thu a vawh hi.
Mark 4:15 Mi pawlkhatte lam gei a a tu khaici tawh kibang uh hi. Amaute in thu a zak uh ciangin thakhatin Satan hong pai in amaute lungsim sunga kivawhsa thu a lakkhiatsak hi.
Mark 4:16 Tua mah bangin pawlkhatte suang laka a tu khaici tawh kibang uh hi. Amaute in thu a zak uh ciangin lungdamtakin sang pah uh a,
