Mark 4:18 Tu in hihte in ling laka a tu khaicite ahi uh hi. Amaute in thu a za mite hi uh a,
Mark 4:19 leitung nuntak nading lunghimawh in khemna tawh kidim na dang tuamtuamte a lunggulh mite ahi uh hi. Tua nate in a zaksa uh thu depgawp ahih manin a gah zo kei uh hi.
Mark 4:20 Ahi zongin hihte in lei hoihna ah a tu khaici ahi uh hi. Amaute in thu a zak uh ciangin sang uh a, pawlkhatte a zah 30, pawlkhatte a zah 60, pawlkhatte a zah 100 a gah uh hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 4:21 ¶ Amah in amaute kiangah a genbeh in ah, “Note in lawh a khuh ding le lupna nuai a koih ding peuhin meivak vak ngei na hi uh hiam? Meivak tunna tungah koih zaw hi lo na hi uh hiam?
