Mark 4:23 Zak nading bil a nei mi in za tahen!” a ci hi.
Mark 4:24 ¶ Tua ciangin amah in amaute tungah a genin ah, “Na thu zak uh limtakin ngaihsun un. Note zat seeng mah tawh no aa dingin hong kitehsakkik ding hi. Hih thu a za note tungah a tamzaw in a hong kipia ding hi.
Mark 4:25 Banghang hiam cihleh a neite kipiak beh ding a, a nei lote a neih sunsun nangawn a kilakkhiatsak ding hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 4:26 ¶ Tua ciangin amah in, “Pasian kumpigam in leilak ah khaici a vawh mipa tawh kibang hi.
Mark 4:27 Tua pa, sun tawh zan tawh ihmu zel, tho zel a, ama theih loh kalin khaici poin a khang hi.
Mark 4:28 Leitang in ama thu in gah a gahsak hi. A masa in hong ngum a, tua khit ciangin hong vui in a vui sungah a tak hong dim hi.
Mark 4:29 A min ciangin at hunta ahih manin a phiaukawi tawh a at pah hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 4:30 ¶ Tua ciangin amah in, “Pasian kumpigam bang tawh kibang a, bang tawh genteh ding i hi hiam?
Mark 4:31 Pasian kumpigam in ankamtang tawh kibang hi. Ankamtang in lei ah a kivawh laitakin leitung a khaici khempeuh lakah a tang neupen hi a,
Mark 4:32 ahih hangin a kivawh khit ciangin a kung hong po in, khai kung khempeuh sangin golzaw a, a mengkhia a hiangte golpipi hong pha hi. Tua ciangin vana leng vasate in a hiang kawm ah bu a tom thei uh hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 4:33 ¶ Amah in amaute theih zawh dingin tua bang thugentehna tampi tawh a hilh hi.
Mark 4:34 Amaute kiangah thugentehna loin thu a hilh kei hi. Ahih hangin ama nungzuite bek tawh a om ciangin thu khempeuh teltakin a hilh hi.
Mark 4:35 ¶ Tua ni nitak lamin amah in a nungzuite kiangah, “Galkhat lamah galkah ni,” a ci hi.
Mark 4:36 ¶ Tu in amaute in mi honpite a nusiat khit uh ciangin Zeisu a na tuanna sa gunkuang tawh amah a paipih uh hi. Gunkuangneu dangte zong amaute tawh a paikhawm uh hi.
Mark 4:37 Tua laitakin huihpi nakpi in hong nung a, tuihual in gunkuang vatgawp ahih manin gunkuang tui sungah a tum dekdek hi.
Mark 4:38 Ahih hangin Zeisu in gunkuang taw lamah lukham khat kham in a ihmu hi. Tua ciangin a nungzuite in amah phong uh a, “Sia aw, simang khin le ung phamawh sa lo na hi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
Mark 4:39 ¶ Tua ciangin amah tho in huihpi taii a, tuipi kiangah, “Dai inla om hithiat in,” ci in thu a pia hi. Tua ciangin huihpi khawlin a dai dide pah hi.
Mark 4:40 ¶ Amah in amaute kiangah, “Banghang in hi zahtakin lau zawzen na hi uh hiam? Banghang in upna nei lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi.
