Mark 5:1 ¶ Amaute in tuili galkhat a om Gadara mite teenna kuam a tung uh hi.
Mark 5:2 Gunkuang tung pan Zeisu a tuahkhiat ciangin dawigilo a vei mi khat han panin hong paikhia in thakhatin Zeisu a na dawntuah hi.
Mark 5:3 Tua pa han lakah teeng a, sikkhau nangawn tawh kuamah in a hen zo kei hi.
Mark 5:4 ¶ Banghang hiam cihleh sikkhau tawh tam veipi khih in kol a kibulh hangin a sikkhau bottat in a kol zong peksat a, kuamah in a zo zo kei hi.
Mark 5:5 Han lak le mual tung ah sun le zanin om tawntung a, kiko niloh in amah le amah suang tawh a kikuiliam gawp hi.
Mark 5:6 ¶ Tua pa in Zeisu a galmuh ciangin ama kiangah tai in a bia hi.
Mark 5:7 Amah nakpi in kiko a, “A Sangbel Pasian Tapa Zeisu aw, nang tawh ka kisaina bang om ahi hiam? Kei nong bawlsiat loh nadingin Pasian minin kong thum hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 5:8 ¶ Banghang hiam cihleh Zeisu in, “Nang dawigilo aw, ama sung pan paikhia in,” ci in thu a pia zo hi.
Mark 5:9 ¶ Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Na min bang ahi hiam?” ci in a dot ciangin amah in, “Kote tampi ka hih manun ka min Legion ahi hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 5:10 ¶ Zeisu in tua gam panin amah a hawlkhiat loh nadingin tua pa in nakpitakin a thum hi.
Mark 5:11 Tu in tua mun tawh a kinai mualte tungah vok honpi khat kicing in a om hi.
Mark 5:12 Tua ciangin dawi gilote khempeuh in Zeisu kiangah, “Vok honte sungah ka lut theih nadingun hong sawl in,” ci in a thum uh hi.
Mark 5:13 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in a phal pah hi. Dawigilote paikhia in vokte sungah a lut uh hi. Tua ciangin vok honte ken lakah taisuk gawp uh a, tui sung kidenna in a si khin uh hi. Tua vok honte 2,000 bang a pha hi.
Mark 5:14 ¶ Tua ciangin vok cingte tai pah vingveng uh a, khua sung le gam sung tengah hih thu a va gen uh ciangin tua thupiang en dingin khua mite a hong paikhia uh hi.
Mark 5:15 Zeisu kiangah a tun uh ciangin dawigilo legion khat a lutna mipa, puansilh in lungsim ngeina pua in tu hithiat a om a mu uh hi. Tua ciangin amaute a lau uh hi.
Mark 5:16 Dawi a lutna pa le vokte tunga thupiang a mu mite in tua khua mite kiangah a gensawn uh hi.
Mark 5:17 Tua khit ciangin tua gam panin Zeisu a paikhiat nadingin tua mite in a ngen uh hi.
Mark 5:18 ¶ Gunkuang sungah Zeisu a kah ciangin dawi a lutna mipa in Zeisu zui nuamin a kun hi.
Mark 5:19 Ahih hangin Zeisu in sang loin ama kiangah, “Na inn ah ciah inla Topa in na lianpi hong bawlnate le hong hehpihnate na lawmte kiangah va gen in,” ci in a sawl hi.
Mark 5:20 ¶ Tua pa pai in Zeisu in ama tunga a bawl na lianpite Decapolis gam sung tengah kizelsak a, mi khempeuh in lamdang a sa uh hi.
Mark 5:21 ¶ Tu in gunkuang tungah Zeisu tuangin a gal khat ah a galkahkik khit ciangin mi honpite a hong kikhawm uh hi.
Mark 5:22 Amah tuili gei ah a om laitakin en in, kikhopna inn ukte lakah Jairus kici mi khat hong pai a, Zeisu a muh ciangin a khephung ah bokin
Mark 5:23 nakpitak thum a, “Ka tanuno si dekdek hi. Amah cidam a hong nuntak theih nadingin hong pai inla a tungah na khut hong ngaksak in,” a ci hi.
Mark 5:24 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in amah zui a, mi honpi in zong Zeisu paina zui uh ahih manin a phu kha gawp uh hi.
Mark 5:25 Tualai ah kum sawm le kum nih sung siluang natna a vei numei khat a om hi.
Mark 5:26 Gimna tampi thuakin siavuan tampi zong kibawlsak a, a neihsa teng nangawn a beita hi. Ahih hangin noptuam cih thadah a gim zaw semsem hi.
Mark 5:27 Tua nu in Zeisu thu a zak ciangin mi honpi lakah hong lut a, a nung lam pan zuanin Zeisu puan a lawng hi.
Mark 5:28 Banghang hiam cihleh tua nu in, “A puan va lawng beek leng zong ka dam ding hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 5:29 ¶ A lawn khit phetin tua nu a siluang kang pah a, a natna a dam lam ama sungah a kithei hi.
Mark 5:30 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in ama sung pan vangliatna paikhia hi cih thei in mi honpi lamah thakhatin kihei a, “Kua in ka puan hong lawng ahi hiam?” a ci hi.
