Mark 5:35 ¶ Amah a paupau laitakin kikhopna inn ukpa inn pana hong paite hong tung uh a, “Na tanu si zo hi; banghang in Siapa buaisak lai ding na hiam?” a ci uh hi.
Mark 5:36 ¶ Zeisu in tua thu a zak phetin kikhopna inn ukpa kiangah, “Patau kei inla um in,” a ci hi.
Mark 5:37 ¶ Zeisu in Peter, James le a sanggampa John longal kuamah dang a kizuisak kei hi.
Mark 5:38 Tua ciangin kikhopna inn ukpa inn ah Zeisu a tun ciangin mite kap le mau a om ngeingai a mu hi.
Mark 5:39 Zeisu inn sungah luta amaute kiangah, “Banghang in mau in kap ngeingai na hi uh hiam? Numeino a si hi loin a ihmu ahi hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 5:40 ¶ Tua ciangin tua mite in amah zahpihin a nuihsan uh hi. Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute a vekpi un pusuaksak a, numeino nu le pa le ama tonpih mite a sap khit ciangin numeino lupna inndei sungah a lut uh hi.
