Mark 6:5 ¶ Cina tawmkhatte tungah a khut nga in a damsak simloh, tua munah nalamdang bangmah a bawl thei kei hi.
Mark 6:6 Amah in amaute up lohna uh lamdang a sa hi.
Mark 6:7 ¶ Tua khit ciangin sawm le nihte ama kiangah sam a, nihta nihta in a sawlkhia hi. Dawigilote tungah thuneihna a pia hi.
Mark 6:8 ¶ Amah in amaute kiangah khualzinna ah a zat ding uh ciangkhut simloh thungip ahi a, an ahi a, sumbawm sungah sum ahi zongin bangmah a ken loh nading uh le
Mark 6:9 khedap bulh in puanak a silh thuah loh nading uh thu a pia hi.
Mark 6:10 Tua ciangin amaute kiangah, “Inn khatpeuh ah na tun uh ciangin tua khua pan na paikhiat matengun tua inn ah tamsuak un.
Mark 6:11 Note hong sang nuam loin na thugen uh zong a ngai nuam lo mite khua pan na paikhiat uh ciangin note khenuai a leivuite singkhia un. Tua leivuite in amaute langkhat ah teci a suak ding hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, thukhen ni ciangin Sodom le Gomorrah khua mite thuakna in tua khua mite thuakna sangin thuak nop zawlai ding hi,” a ci hi.
