Mark 6:14 ¶ Tu in, Zeisu minthang mahmah ahih manin Kumpipa Herod in ama thu a za hi. Tua ciangin amah in, “Tuiphumpa John misite lak pan hong thokik zo a, hih vangliatnate amah in a nei ahi hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 6:15 ¶ Mi pawlkhat in, “Hihpa Elijah ahi hi,” a ci uh hi. A dangte in, “Kamsangpa khat ahih keileh kamsangte khatpeuh tawh a kibang mi khat ahi hi,” a ci uh hi.
Mark 6:16 ¶ Ahih hangin Herod in a zak ciangin, “A ngawng ka tansa John mah misite lak pan hong thokik ahi hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 6:17 ¶ Herod in a sanggampa Philip zi Herodias a teenpihna thu tawh kisai in John in Herod a mawhsak ngei hi. Tua ahih manin Herod in John mansak a, sikkhau tawh khih in thongah a khum hi.
Mark 6:18 Banghang hiam cihleh John in Herod kiangah, “Na sanggampa zi na teenpih pen thukham tawh kituak lo hi,” ci in a gen manin tua banga a khum ahi hi.
Mark 6:19 ¶ Tua ahih manin Herodias in John mudah in a that nuam hi. Ahih hangin tua numei in a that thei kei hi.
Mark 6:20 Banghang hiam cihleh Herod in John kihta a, John pen mi dik misiangtho ahihlam Herod in thei ahih manin amah a huu hi. John thugente in Herod lungsim buaisak mahmah a, ahih hangin a thugente hoih a sa mahmah hi.
