Mark 6:23 Ka gam phelkhat dongin nong nget peuhpeuh kong pia ding hi,” ci in kiciam in kamciam a pia hi.
Mark 6:24 ¶ Tua ciangin nungakno paikhia in a nu kiangah, “Bang ngen ding ka hi hiam?” ci in a dong hi. ¶ A nu in, “Tuiphumpa John lutang va ngen in,” a ci hi.
Mark 6:25 ¶ Nungakno zong hong kilehkik pah vingveng in kumpipa kiangah, “Tuiphumpa John lutang kuangdai sung khat ah hong pia pah leteh ka ut hi,” a ci hi.
