Mark 6:31 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Gamdaihna mun khat ah pai unla, tawmvei sung tawlnga un,” a ci hi. ¶ Mi a ciah le a kuan kiphamat in annek hun ding nangawn ngah lo uh ahih manin tua banga a gen ahi hi.
Mark 6:32 Tua ciangin amaute gunkuang khat tawh gamdaihna mun khat ah tuam paikhiat uh hi.
Mark 6:33 Tu in amaute paikhiat mi honpi in mu uh a, mi tampi in Zeisu zong a kihel lam thei uh ahih manin khua khempeuh panin khe tawh hong tai ngeingai uh hi. Zeisu tun ma in tua mun na tungkhol uh a, Zeisu hong tun ciangin a kiangah hong kikhawm uh hi.
Mark 6:34 Gunkuang sung pan Zeisu hong tuahkhiat ciangin mi honpite mu a, a cing om lo tuute tawh kibang uh ahih manin hehpihhuai sa in tua munah amaute thu tampi a hilh hi.
Mark 6:35 ¶ Nitum kuan ciangin nungzuite ama kiangah hong pai uh a, “Hih mun in gamlakpi hi a, ni zong tum dekta hi.
Mark 6:36 Hih mite in annek ding bangmah nei lo uh ahih manin, an lei dingin hih kima om khuaneute ah paisak in,” a ci uh hi.
Mark 6:37 ¶ Tua ciangin amah in, “Amaute nek theih khat peuhpeuh pia un,” a ci hi. ¶ Nungzuite in, “Kote pai in denarius 200 man an lei in a nek ding uh pia ding ka hi uh hiam?” a ci uh hi.
Mark 6:38 ¶ Amah in, “Anlum bangzah nei na uh hiam? Pai unla va en dih un,” a ci hi. ¶ Amaute in a omzah a theih khit uh ciangin, “Anlum nga le ngasa nih om hi,” a ci uh hi.
Mark 6:39 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in mi khempeuh lopa tungah a honhon in tusak un ci in a sawl hi.
