Mark 6:45 ¶ Zeisu in mi honpi a ciahsak laitakin nungzuite gunkuang ah tuangsak mengmeng a, galkhat a om Bethsaida khua ah a mapaisak hi.
Mark 6:46 Amaute a ciahkhiatsak khit ciangin thungen dingin mual tung ah a paito hi.
Mark 6:47 ¶ Tu in nitak hong tun ciangin tuili laizang ah gunkuang om a, tuili gei leitang tungah Zeisu bek a om hi.
Mark 6:48 Tua ciangin huih lehnun ahih manin nungzuite in haksapi in gunkuang a hot uh Zeisu in a mu hi. Zanvil lina hun pawlin amaute kiang zuanin Zeisu tui tungah hong pai a, amaute a kheng dektak hi.
Mark 6:49 Amah tui tunga hong pai amaute in a muh uh ciangin, sikha sa in a kiko uh hi.
Mark 6:50 Banghang hiam cihleh a vekpi un amah mu uh a, a patau uh hi. ¶ Ahi zongin Zeisu in, “Lungnuam un! Keimah ka hi hi. Lau kei un,” a ci hi.
Mark 6:51 ¶ Tua ciangin amaute tuanna gunkuang ah Zeisu a kahtoh khit ciangin huih a dai hi. Amaute in gen zawh loh zahin lamdang a sa uh hi.
Mark 6:52 Banghang hiam cihleh a lungtang uh khauhlua ahih manin anlum tawh nalamdang a bawlna thu a ngaihsun kha kei uh hi.
Mark 6:53 ¶ A galkhat ah a kah khit uh ciangin Gennesaret gam ah a pai uh a, tuili gei ah gunkuang a khih uh hi.
