Mark 7:1 ¶ Tua khit ciangin Jerusalem khuapi pana hong pai Phariseete le thukhamhilh siate pawlkhat Zeisu kiangah hong paikhawm uh hi.
Mark 7:2 Tu in a nungzuite kimkhat in khut ninsa a an a nek uh amaute in a muh uh ciangin a mawhsak uh hi. Khutnin a cih ciangin khutsil lo cihna ahi hi.
Mark 7:3 Banghang hiam cihleh Phariseete le Judah mi khempeuh in tanglai mite ngeina zui uh a, khutsil loin an ne lo uh hi.
Mark 7:4 Sumbuuk pan a ciah uh ciangin zong kisil loin an ne lo uh hi. Haite, belte, sumngo kuangte le sabuaite sawpsiangna ngeina a kipan zuih ding a dang ngeina tampi zong neilai uh hi.
Mark 7:5 ¶ Tua ciangin Pharisee pawlte le thukhamhilh siate in ama kiangah, “Na nungzuite in tanglai mite ngeina zui loin banghang in khutsil lopi in an ne uh ahi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi.
Mark 7:6 ¶ Amah in amaute kiangah, “A kineihkhem note thu, kamsangpa Isaiah in Lai Siangtho sunga a genkholhna thu a man hi. Amah in, ‘Hih mite in a kam uh tawh a hong pahtawi uh hangin, A lungsim uh kei tawh kigamla hi.
Mark 7:7 Mihing bawltawm thukhamte thuhilhna in zang uh ahih manin, Kei a hong biakna uh a mawkna ahi hi,’ a ci hi.
Mark 7:8 ¶ “Banghang hiam cihleh Pasian thupiakte nawlkhin in tanglai ngeina ahi bel le kuang sawpsiangna a kipan tua bang a dang ngeina tampi na zui uh hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 7:9 ¶ Amaute kiangah, “Tanglai ngeina na zuih theih nadingun Pasian thupiak na nawlkhin uh a, tua banga na hih uh ciangin hi na kisa mahmah uh hi.
Mark 7:10 Moses in, ‘Na nu le na pa zahtak in,’ ci a, ‘A nu ahi a, a pa ahi zongin a samsia mi in thahna thuak tahen,’ ci in note thu hong pia hi.
Mark 7:11 ¶ “Ahih hangin, ‘Note in mi khat in a nu le a pa kiangah, “Kei tung pana na ngah ding khempeuh Corban hita hi,” ci peuh leh bangmah a piak kul nawn kei hi,’ na ci uh hi. Corban a khiatna in Pasian kipia khin cihna ahi hi.
Mark 7:12 Tua bang thu tawh a nu le a pa aa dingin tua pa in bangmah sep kul nawn lo hi na ci uh hi.
Mark 7:13 Note in na kihilh sawnsawn uh tanglai ngeinate zui in Pasian thu kimanna nei lo na suaksak uh a, tua bang dan ngeina tampi na nei uh hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 7:14 ¶ Amah in mi honpite a sap khit ciangin amaute kiangah, “Na vekpi un ka thugen ngai unla thei un.
Mark 7:15 A pualam panin mihing sunga tumsuk na khat beek in mi a ninsak thei kei hi. Mihing sung pana a pusuakkhiate bekin mihing a ninsak hi.
Mark 7:16 Zak nading bil a nei mi in za tahen!” a ci hi.
Mark 7:17 ¶ Mi honpi lak pan amah paikhia a, inn sungah a lut khit ciangin a nungzuite in tua thugentehna thu a dong uh hi.
Mark 7:18 Tua ciangin amah in amaute kiangah, “Note in zong tel lo na hi uh hiam? A pualam pan mihing sunga a tumsuk peuhmah in mi a ninsak thei kei hi.
Mark 7:19 Banghang hiam cihleh lungsim sungah lut loin gilpi sungah lut a, a kine an khempeuh kithakhia in kisiangthosak hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 7:20 ¶ Amah in, “Mihing sung pana pusuakte in tuami a ninsak hi.
Mark 7:21 Banghang hiam cihleh a sunglam a om mihingte lungsim panin ngaihsutna hoih lo, angkawmna, numei pasal mawhna, mi thahna,
Mark 7:22 guktakna, duhhopna, gitlohna, khemna, numei pasal paktatna, etsatna, kosiatna, kiphatsakna, haitatnate a hong pusuak hi.
Mark 7:23 Hih a hoih lo thute khempeuh sunglam pan hong pusuakin mihing a ninsak hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 7:24 ¶ Tua khit ciangin tua mun pan amah paikhia a, Tyre le Sidon gam sungah pai in inn khat ah a lut hi. Tualai ah a om lam kuama theih ding a ut loh hangin a kisel zo kei hi.
Mark 7:25 Dawigilo a vei tanu a nei nupi khat in Zeisu thu a zak ciangin hong pai a, Zeisu khephung ah bokin
Mark 7:26 a tanu sung pan dawi gilo a hawlkhiatsak nadingin a ngen den hi. Tua nu pen Syro-Phoenicia gama piang Greek numei khat ahi hi.
Mark 7:27 ¶ Ahih hangin Zeisu in tua nu kiangah, “Tate annek lai lakhia in uite piak ding kilawm lo hi. Tua ahih manin tate ka gilvahsak masa phot ding hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 7:28 ¶ Tua nu in, “Topa aw, hi mah hi. Ahi zongin sabuai nuai a om tate anneng kiate nangawn, uinote in ne kha sam uh hi lo ahi hiam?” ci in a dawng hi.
Mark 7:29 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Tua banga na cih manin na tanu sung pan dawi gilo a taikhia zo hi. Ciahta in,” a ci hi.
Mark 7:30 ¶ Tua nu ama inn a tun ciangin lupna tungah a tanu lum a, ama sung pan dawi gilo paikhia khinzo cih a mu hi.
Mark 7:31 ¶ Tyre le Sidon khua panin Zeisu paikhia leuleu a, Decapolis gam kantan in Galilee tuili a tung hi.
Mark 7:32 Tua ciangin amaute in a bengngong, a pauthei lo mi khat ama kiangah hong paipih uh a, tua pa tungah a khut a ngak nadingin a ngen uh hi.
Mark 7:33 ¶ Zeisu in mi honpi lak panin tua pa paikhiatpih a, a bil langnih sungah a khutme guangin a cil phiha, a lei a lawnsak hi.
Mark 7:34 Tua khit ciangin vantung lam ento in khuisa a, ama kiangah, “Ephphatha,” a ci hi. A khiatna pen, “Kihong in,” a cihna ahi hi.
Mark 7:35 Tua pa thakhatin a bil kihong a, a leiigui zong kikhah in siangtakin a pau thei hi.
Mark 7:36 ¶ Tua ciangin tua thu kuama kiangah a gen loh nadingun Zeisu in thu a pia hi. Ahih hangin nak kham semsem le tua mite in a nak gen semsem uh hi.
Mark 7:37 Amaute in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Amah in na khempeuh a hoih in bawl a, bengngongte khuazasak in pau thei lote a pautheisak hi,” a ci uh hi.
Mark 8:1 ¶ Tua hun sungin mi honpite tamlua mahmah a, nek ding zong a nei kei uh hi. Tua ciangin Zeisu in a nungzuite sam a,
Mark 8:2 “Hih mite ka kiangah ni thum hong om khin uh a, nek ding lah nei lo uh ahih manin hehpihhuai ka sa hi.
