Mark 8:4 ¶ Tua ciangin a nungzuite in, “Kua in mihing hi zahta hih gamlak ah an bangci vak zawh ding ahi hiam?” ci in a dawng uh hi.
Mark 8:5 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Anlum bangzah nei na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. Amaute in, “Sagih a om hi,” a ci uh hi.
Mark 8:6 ¶ Tua ciangin amah in mi honpite leilak ah tu dingin thu a piak khit ciangin anlum sagihte la in lungdam a ko hi. Tuate balnenin mipi lakah hawm dingin a nungzuite pia a, amaute in zong mi honpite lakah a hawm uh hi.
Mark 8:7 Amaute in ngasaneu tawmkha zong a nei uh hi. Amah in tuate thupha a piak khit ciangin mi honpite lakah hawm dingin thu a pia hi.
Mark 8:8 Tua ciangin amaute in a kham dong uh a nek khit uh ciangin a khamval uh a them a nengin kaikhawm uh a, lawhbeu sagih a ngah uh hi.
Mark 8:9 Tu in an a ne mi 4,000 bang a pha uh hi. Tua khit ciangin amah in amaute ciahsak in,
Mark 8:10 thakhat thu in nungzuite tawh gunkuang tung tuangin Dalmanutha gam ah a pai uh hi.
Mark 8:11 ¶ Tua ciangin Pharisee pawlte hong pai in Zeisu thugen nial dingin a kipan uh hi. Amah a ze-etna un, “Vantung panin limlamdang khat hong lak in,” ci in a ngen uh hi.
Mark 8:12 Ahih hangin a lungsim sungah Zeisu nakpi in khuisa a, “Banghang in tulai khang mite in nalamdang mu nuam uh ahi hiam? A man takpi kong cihin ah, tulai khang mite tungah limlamdang a kilak kei ding hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 8:13 ¶ Amah in amaute nusia in gunkuang tuangkik a, galkhat lamah a paikhia hi.
Mark 8:14 ¶ Tu in a nungzuite in anlum puak ding mangngilh uh a, gunkuang sungah anlum khat longal a dang bangmah a nei kei uh hi.
Mark 8:15 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Phariseete silngo le Herod silngo kidawm unla pelh un,” ci in thu a pia hi.
Mark 8:16 ¶ Amaute in, “Anlum i neih loh manin hih banga hong ci ahi hi,” ci in a kikum uh hi.
Mark 8:17 ¶ Tua banga thu a kikup uh Zeisu in a theih ciangin, “Anlum na neih loh manun banghang in tua bangin kikum na hi uh hiam? Phawk thei nai lo, tel thei nai lo na hi uh hiam? Na lungtang uh khauhsak lailai na hi uh hiam?
Mark 8:18 Mittang nei napi khuamu lo na hi uh hiam? Bil nei napi khuaza lo na hi uh hiam? Phawk thei mahmah lo na hi uh hiam?
Mark 8:19 ¶ “Mi 5,000 aa dingin anlum nga ka balkhap ciangin a kikhamval an lawh bangzah ngah na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. ¶ Amaute in, “Lawh sawm le lawh nih,” a ci uh hi.
Mark 8:20 ¶ “Mi 4,000 aa dingin anlum sagih ka balkhap ciangin a kikhamval lawhbeu bangzah ngah na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. ¶ Amaute in, “Lawhbeu sagih,” a ci uh hi.
Mark 8:21 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Tua ahih leh bang dinga hih thu tel zo lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi.
Mark 8:22 ¶ Tua ciangin amah Bethsaida khua ah hong tung a, mite in ama kiangah mittaw khat hong paipihin tua pa a lawn nadingin a thum uh hi.
Mark 8:23 Tua ciangin amah in mittawpa a khut in kai a, khuanawl ah a paipih hi. Tua khit ciangin a mit cil phihsak in a tungah a khut a ngakh khit ciangin, “Na khatpeuh na mu thei ta hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
Mark 8:24 ¶ Tua pa khuadak in, “Mite ka et ciangin singkung lampai bangin ka mu hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 8:25 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in tua pa mit tungah a khut khatvei nga kik a, tua khit ciangin a khuadaksak hi. A mit a ngei bangin hoihkik a, mi khempeuh teltakin a mu thei hi.
Mark 8:26 Tua ciangin amah in tua pa a inn ah ciahsak a, ama kiangah, “Khua sungah lut kei inla, hih thu kuama kiangah gen kei in,” ci in thu a pia hi.
