Mark 14:36 Amah in, “ Abba,Pa aw, nang aa dingin na khempeuh piang thei ahih manin hih hai tawh hong kipelhsak in. Ahi zongin kei deihna bang hi loin nangma deihna bang hi zaw tahen,” a ci hi.
Mark 14:37 ¶ Tua ciangin a nungzuite kiang a tun ciangin amaute ihmu in a om a mu hi. Amah in Peter kiangah, “Simon aw, ihmu na hi hiam? Nai khat sung nangawn hong ngak zo lo na hi hiam?
Mark 14:38 Ze-etna sungah na lut khak loh nadingun thungenin kiging un. Lungsim a ut mahmah hangin pumpi a thanem hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 14:39 ¶ Amah va paikhiakikin thungen a, a nget ngei teng mah a va ngen hi.
Mark 14:40 Hong kilehkik ciangin hak zo mahmah lo uh ahih manin ihmukik in a om uh a mu hi. Amaute in amah a dawn nading mel a thei kei uh hi.
Mark 14:41 ¶ A thumveina hong pai ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “lhmu mu lai in, tawlnga lailai ding na hi uh hiam? Phazo hi. A hun hong tungta hi. En un, Mihing Tapa mawhneite khut sungah hong kilehhek ding hun hong tung zo hi.
Mark 14:42 Tho unla pai ni. En un, kei hong lehhekpa hong nai mahmah ta hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 14:43 ¶ Amah tua banga a gengen laitakin sawm le nihte lakah khat ahi Judas le namsau le molhtum a tawi mi honpi thakhatin hong suak uh hi. Tua mite pen siampi liante, thukhamhilh siate le makaite sawl ahi uh hi.
Mark 14:44 ¶ Tu in a lehhekpa in, “Ka nap mipa amah ahi hi. Man unla lencip in paikhiatpih un,” ci in amaute theihsakna lim khat a piaksa ahi hi.
Mark 14:45 ¶ Amah a hong tun phetin Zeisu kiang naih a, “ Rabbi,Rabbi,” ci in a nam hi.
Mark 14:46 ¶ Tua ciangin amaute in Zeisu manin a paikhiatpih uh hi.
Mark 14:47 Ama kianga a ding mi khat in a namsau dokin Siampi Ukpa nasempa a sat leh a bil a satkhia hi.
Mark 14:48 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Guta buluh khat man ding bangin namsau le molhtumte tawi in kei hong man dingin hong kuan na hi uh hiam?
Mark 14:49 Nisimin biakinnpi huang sungah thu hilhin note tawh ka om a, nong man kei uh hi. Ahih hangin Lai Siangtho a tangtun loh phamawh hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 14:50 ¶ Tua ciangin amaute khempeuh in amah nusia in a taikek uh hi.
Mark 14:51 Tu in dialkang khat bek a silh tangvalno khat in Zeisu nung a zui hi. Mihon laka tangval dangte in tua pa a mat uh ciangin,
Mark 14:52 tua pa in a dialkang nusia in a guaktangin a taikhia hi.
Mark 14:53 ¶ Amaute in Siampi Ukpa kiangah Zeisu a paipih uh hi. Tua Siampi Ukpa kiangah siampi liante, makaite le thukhamhilh siate khempeuh a na kikaikhawm uh hi.
Mark 14:54 Peter in Siampi Ukpa inntual dongin Zeisu galzuih a, tua munah biakinn cingte tawh tukhawm in mei a awi hi.
Mark 14:55 ¶ Tu in siampi liante le thukhente khempeuh in Zeisu thah theih nading teci a zon uh hangin khat beek a mu zo kei uh hi.
Mark 14:56 Banghang hiam cihleh mi tampi in Zeisu langah zuau teci a pan uh hangin a tecipannate uh khat le khat a kituak kei hi.
Mark 14:57 ¶ Tua ciangin mi pawlkhat dingto in ama langah zuau teci a pang uh hi.
Mark 14:58 Amaute in, “Hihpa in, ‘Khut tawh kibawl hih biakinnpi ka susia ding a, khut tawh kibawl lo a dang biakinnpi khat ni thum sungin ka lamkik ding hi,’ a cih ka za uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
Mark 14:59 ¶ Ahih hangin tua thu nangawn ah amaute tecipanna a kituak kei hi.
Mark 14:60 Tua ciangin amaute laizang ah Siampi Ukpa dingto in Zeisu kiangah, “Kam khat beek dawng lo ding na hi hiam? Na langa hih mite tecipanna bang thu ahi hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
Mark 14:61 ¶ Ahih hangin Zeisu in bangmah dawng loin a sip dide hi. Siampi Ukpa in, “Phatna a Ngahpa Tapa, Khazih na hi hiam?” ci in a dongkik hi.
Mark 14:62 ¶ Zeisu in, “Ka hi hi. Ahi zongin nang tungah kong genin ah, Vangliatna taklam ah Mihing Tapa tu in vana meiipi tawh a hong paina mailam ah na mu ding hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 14:63 ¶ Tua ciangin Siampi Ukpa in a puan balkek a, “Teci dang bang kisam nawn i hi hiam?
Mark 14:64 Pasian tunga a pausiatna na za zo uh hi. Bangci ngaihsut na hi hiam?” a ci hi. ¶ Amaute khempeuh in, “Amah a si dingin kilawm hi,” ci in a mawhsak uh hi.
Mark 14:65 Tua ciangin pawlkhat in amah cil a phih uh hi. A mai tunsak in tum uh a, “Kamsanna tawh hong gen dih in,” a ci uh hi. Biakinn cingte in zong a beng uh hi.
Mark 14:66 ¶ Inntual ah Peter a om laitakin Siampi Ukpa nasem numei khat ama kiangah a hong pai hi.
Mark 14:67 Tua nu in mei-awi a om Peter a muh ciangin en a, “Nang zong Nazareth khua mi Zeisu pawl na hi hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 14:68 ¶ Ahih hangin Peter in, “Na gen thu, ka thei kei a, zong ka tel kei hi,” ci in a nial hi. ¶ Tua ciangin amah inn pualam zuanin paikhia a, aak a khuang hi.
Mark 14:69 Tua ciangin tua nasem numei in amah va mukik a, a kianga a ding mite kiangah, “Hih mipa in amaute lakah khat ahi hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 14:70 ¶ Tua ciangin Peter in a nialkik hi. Tua zawh a sawt loin ama kianga a ding mite in, “Nangin amaute lakah khat na hi takpi hi. Galilee mi na hih lam na awkaihin kithei hi,” a cikik uh hi.
Mark 14:71 ¶ Ahih hangin Peter in, “Na genpa uh ka thei kei hi,” ci in amah le amah kihamsiat in a kiciam hi.
Mark 14:72 ¶ Tua ciangin a nihveina aak a khuang hi. Zeisu in, “Aak nihvei a khuan ma in thumvei nong nial ding hi,” ci in a gen thu Peter in phawkkik ahih manin a kapkhia hi.
Mark 15:1 ¶ Zingsang tungin siampi liante in makaite, thukhamhilh siate le thukhente khempeuh tawh thakhatin thu kikupna khat a nei uh hi. Amaute in Zeisu henin, paikhiatpih uh a, Pilate khut ah a pia uh hi.
Mark 15:2 ¶ Tua ciangin Pilate mangpipa in, “Nang Judah mite Kumpipa na hi hiam?” ci in a dong hi. ¶ Zeisu in, “Na cih bangin ka hi hi,” ci in a dawng hi.
Mark 15:3 ¶ Siampi liante in thu tampi tawh a mawhmat uh hangin Zeisu in kam khat beek a dawng kei hi.
Mark 15:4 Tua ciangin Pilate mangpipa in, “Na langah hihzah taka hong kimawhmatna thu za khin na hih ciangin kam khat beek dawng lo ding na hi hiam?” ci in a dongkik hi.
Mark 15:5 ¶ Ahih hangin Zeisu in a dawn loh ciangin Pilate in lamdang a sa mahmah hi.
Mark 15:6 ¶ Tu in pawi hun ciangin Pilate in thongkiate lak panin amaute nget penpen mi khat a khahsak zel pen ngeina khat ahi hi.
Mark 15:7 Tua laitakin Barabbas a kici mi khat, kumpi a langpanpih a lawmte tawh thong sungah kol kibulh in a om hi. Amaute in kumpi langpang in mi a thatte ahi uh hi.
Mark 15:8 Tua ciangin mi honpite nakpitak kiko in Pilate in ahih ngei banga mi khat a khahsak nadingin a ngen uh hi.
Mark 15:9 ¶ Ahih hangin Pilate in, “Judah mite Kumpipa hong khah leng na ut uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
Mark 15:10 ¶ Banghang hiam cihleh siampi liante in Zeisu a hazat manun ama kiangah a piakkhiat uh ahihlam Pilate in a thei gige hi.
Mark 15:11 Ahih hangin siampi liante in mi honpite hansuah uh a, Pilate in Barabbas a khah zawk nading a ngensak uh hi.
Mark 15:12 ¶ Tua ciangin Pilate in, “Tua ahih leh, Judah mite Kumpipa hi na cihpa uh bang kong cihsak ding deih na hi uh hiam?” a cikik hi.
Mark 15:13 ¶ Amaute in, “Amah khailum in!” ci in a kikokik uh hi.
Mark 15:14 ¶ Tua ciangin Pilate in amaute kiangah, “Banghang in khailum ding ka hi hiam? Amah in bang siatna bawl ahi hiam?” ci in a gen hi. Ahi zongin amaute in, “Amah khailum in!” ci in a kiko semsem uh hi.
Mark 15:15 ¶ Tua hi a, Pilate in mi honpi a lungkim sak nadingin Barabbas khahsak a, Zeisu ahih leh a satsak khit ciangin khailup dingin a pia hi.
Mark 15:16 ¶ Tua ciangin galkapte in mangpipa inn ah Zeisu paipih uh a, galkaphon khempeuh zong a kaikhawm uh hi.
Mark 15:17 Amaute in puan dupsan khat silhsak uh a, linglukhu a khusak uh hi.
Mark 15:18 Tua khit ciangin, “Judah mite Kumpipa aw, na ci dam tahen!” ci in a hopih uh hi.
Mark 15:19 Pumpeng tawh a lutang satin cilphih uh a, khukdinin a bia uh hi.
Mark 15:20 A zahko khit uh ciangin puan dupsan pen suahkhiatsak in ama puan silhsakkik uh a, khailup dingin a paikhiatpih uh hi.
Mark 15:21 ¶ Tua laitakin Alexander le Rufus-te pa Cyrene mi Simon khualzin hong ciah tawh a kituak uh hi. Amaute in zawhthawhthu tawh amah manin Zeisu singlamteh a puasak uh hi.
Mark 15:22 Luguh Mun cih khiatna nei, Golgotha kici munah amah a paipih uh hi.
Mark 15:23 Tua ciangin paknamtui kha tawh kihel lenggahzu dawn dingin a piak uh hangin Zeisu in a dawn kei hi.
Mark 15:24 Amaute in Zeisu a khai khit uh ciangin a puante hawm uh a, amau tan ding ciat a theih nadingun lai-ai a san uh hi.
Mark 15:25 ¶ Tu in nai thum sat a, amaute in amah a khailum uh hi.
Mark 15:26 A lu tung sanah “JUDAH MITE KUMPIPA,” ci in mawhsakna lai khat a suang uh hi.
Mark 15:27 Guta nih zong a taklam ah khat, a veilam ah khat, amah tawh a khaikhawm uh hi.
Mark 15:28 Hih bangin, Lai Siangtho sunga kigelh ahi, “Thukham palsat mite tawh amah kisimkhawm hi,” a cihna thu a tangtung hi.
Mark 15:29 ¶ Tua mun a tawn kha mite in a lu uh peisan in a zahko uh a, “Hei! Biakinnpi susia a ni thum sungin a lam kik ding pa aw,
Mark 15:30 nangmah kihonkhia inla, singlamteh tung pan hong kumkhia in!” a ci uh hi.
Mark 15:31 ¶ Tua mah bangin siampi liante le thukhamhilh siate in zong zahko in, “Hihpa in midangte hon zo napi amah le amah a kihonkhia zo kei hi.
Mark 15:32 I mit mahmah tawh mu a, i up theih nadingin Israel Kumpipa Khazih singlamteh tung panin tu in hong kumkhia hen,” a ci uh hi. ¶ Amah tawh a kikhaikhawm mite in zong a zahko uh hi.
Mark 15:33 ¶ Tu in nai guk a kipan nai kua ciangdong leitung bup ah khim a zing hi.
Mark 15:34 Nai kua a sat laitakin Zeisu in, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabachthani?” ci in nakpi in a kiko hi. A khiatna in, Ka Pasian, ka Pasian aw, banghang in hong nusia na hi hiam? a cihna ahi hi.
Mark 15:35 ¶ A gei a a ding mite pawlkhat in a zak uh ciangin, “En un, amah in Elijah a sam ahi hi!” a ci uh hi.
Mark 15:36 ¶ Tua ciangin mi khat va tai a, tuihupna khat la in lenggahtui thuk a dimtakin a diah khit ciangin, pumpeng dawn ah suangin a dawn dingin tahto a, “Hi ci omsak tadih un. Amah lakhia dingin Elijah hong pai hiam, en dih ni,” a ci hi.
Mark 15:37 ¶ Tua ciangin Zeisu nakpitak kiko in a huu tawpna a sangkhia hi.
Mark 15:38 ¶ Tua laitakin biakinnpi sunga kideina puan kikek a, a lu panin a taw dong phelnih a suak hi.
Mark 15:39 Zeisu maingat a ding galkap 100 ukpa in amah tua bangin kiko a a huu tawpna a sankhiat a muh ciangin, “Hihpa in Pasian Tapa taktak ahi hi!” a ci hi.
Mark 15:40 ¶ Numei pawlkhat in gamlapi pan galet uh a, tua numeite lakah Magdala khua mi Mary, James neuzaw le Joses-te nu Mary le Salome-te zong a kihel uh hi.
Mark 15:41 Amaute in Galilee gam ah Zeisu a omlai in amah zui in a panpihte ahi uh hi. Jerusalem khuapi dong amah a zui numei dang tampi zong a om uh hi.
Mark 15:42 ¶ Tu in nitak hong hi a, tua ni in Sabbath a tun ma Kigin Ni ahi hi.
Mark 15:43 Tua ciangin Arimathea khua mi Joseph in Pilate kiangah hangtakin va pai a, Zeisu luang a va ngen hi. Amah pen upa vaihawmte lakah mi thupi khat hi a, Pasian kumpigam a lamen mi khat zong ahi hi.
Mark 15:44 Zeisu si khin ahihlam Pilate in a zak ciangin lamdangsa mahmah a, galkap 100 ukpa samin a sih zawh bangtan sawt zo hiam ci in a dong hi.
Mark 15:45 Zeisu si khin hi cih thu Pilate in galkap 100 ukpa kiang pan a theihtel ciangin Zeisu luang Joseph a pia hi.
Mark 15:46 Tua ciangin Joseph in Zeisu luang lakhia a, a hoih mahmah puanpak khat lei in a tun khit ciangin suang kikhuak han sung khat ah sial a, suangtumpi khat khuk in hankong a khak hi.
Mark 15:47 Magdala khua mi Mary le Joses nu Mary-te in a luang kisialna mun a en uh hi.
Mark 16:1 ¶ Tu in Sabbath ni hong bei a, Magdala khua mi Mary, James nu Mary le Salome-te in a luang zut nadingin sathau namtui a lei uh hi.
Mark 16:2 Nipikal sunga ni masa pen ni zingsang nisuah tungin daihawh dingin hanah a hong pai uh hi.
Mark 16:3 “Hankong khakna suangtum kua in hong honsak ding ahi hiam?” ci in a kikum uh hi.
Mark 16:4 ¶ Ahih hangin amaute a khuadak uh leh tua suangtum a kikhukkhiasa a om a mu uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh tua suangtum a lian mahmah khat ahi hi.
Mark 16:5 Han sungah lut uh a, puanpak tualpi a silh tangval khat taklam panga a tu a muh uh ciangin lamdang a sa uh hi.
Mark 16:6 ¶ Ahih hangin tua pa in, “Lamdangsa kei un. A kikhailum Nazareth khua mi Zeisu na zong uh hi. Amah thokik zo hi! Hihlai ah om nawn lo hi. A luang kisialna mun hong en un.
Mark 16:7 Tu in ciah unla Peter le a nungzuite kiangah, ‘Note pai ma in Galilee gam ah na paikhol ding a, a hong gensa bangin tualai ah amah na mu ding uh hi,’ ci in va gen un,” a ci hi.
Mark 16:8 ¶ Amaute han sung panin manlangtakin hong paikhia uh a, a tai uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh amaute lau uh a, lamdang a sa uh hi. Amaute lau uh ahih manin kuamah kiangah thu bangmah a gen kei uh hi.
Mark 16:9 ¶ Tu in nipikal khat sunga ni masa pen ni zingsang tungin Zeisu thokik a, dawi sagih a hawlkhiatna numei Magdala khua mi Mary kiangah a kilak masa pen hi.
Mark 16:10 Tua numei in Zeisu tawh a kithuah khawm ngei, dah le kap a om mite kiangah pai in tua thu a va gen hi.
Mark 16:11 Amah thokik ahihna le Mary in a muhna thu amaute in a zak uh ciangin a um kei uh hi.
Mark 16:12 ¶ Tua khit ciangin nungzuite nih gam sung khuaneu khat ah a pai laitakun amaute kiangah a nam tuamkhat in Zeisu a va kilak hi.
Mark 16:13 Amaute in nungzui dangte a va koh uh hangin a um tuan kei uh hi.
Mark 16:14 ¶ Tua nung ciangin nungzui sawm le khatte an ne a a om laitakun amaute kiangah Zeisu a kilak hi. Amah a thawhkik khit cianga a mu mite thugente um loin lungkhauh uh ahih manin Zeisu in amaute a taii hi.
Mark 16:15 ¶ Amah in amaute kiangah, “Leitung khempeuh ah pai unla a kipiangsak na khempeuh tungah lungdamna thu tangko un.
Mark 16:16 Thu umin tui a kiphum mi in hotkhiatna a ngah ding hi. Ahih hangin a um lo mi in mawhsakna a thuak ding hi.
Mark 16:17 Thu-um mitetungah hih limlamdangte a piang ding hi. Keima min tawh dawite hawlkhia ding uh a, kampau thak tawh a pau ding uh hi.
Mark 16:18 Gulte man ding uh a, sih theihna gu a dawn uh hangin bangmah a ci kei ding uh hi. Cinate tungah khut a ngakh uh ciangin a dam ding uh hi,” a ci hi.
Mark 16:19 ¶ Tua bangin Topa Zeisu in amaute kiangah thu a gen khit ciangin vantung ah amah kilato a, Pasian taklam ah a tu hi.
Mark 16:20 A nungzuite kuankhia in mun khempeuh ah lungdamna thu a tangko uh hi. Topa in amaute tawh na semkhawm a, nalamdangte tawh ama kammal a kipsak hi. Amen.